"To process and scan barcodes for warehouse receipts, navigate to "
"the :menuselection:`Barcode` app."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/barcode/operations/receipts_deliveries.rst:65
msgid ""
"Once inside the **Barcode** app, a :guilabel:`Barcode Scanning` screen "
"displaying different options is presented."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/barcode/operations/receipts_deliveries.rst:71
msgid ""
"To process receipts, click the :guilabel:`Operations` button at the bottom "
"of the screen. The :guilabel:`Operations` overview page opens."
msgstr ""
"Pour traiter les réceptions, cliquer sur le bouton :guilabel:`Opérations` en "
"bas de l'écran. La page de vue d'ensemble :guilabel:`Opérations` s'ouvre."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/barcode/operations/receipts_deliveries.rst:74
msgid ""
"From this page, tap the :guilabel:`Receipts` card to view all outstanding "
"receipts. Then, select the desired receipt operation to process. This "
"navigates to the barcode transfer screen."
msgstr ""
"Depuis cette page, appuyer sur la carte :guilabel:`Réceptions` pour voir "
"toutes les réceptions en attente. Ensuite, sélectionner l'opération de "
"réception souhaitée à traiter. Cela permet d'accéder à l'écran de transfert "
"de code-barres."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/barcode/operations/receipts_deliveries.rst:78
msgid ""
"If *only* using a barcode scanner or the Odoo mobile app, the barcodes for "
"each transfer of a corresponding operation type can be scanned to be "
"processed easily. Once scanned, the products that are part of an existing "
"transfer can be scanned, and new products can be added to the transfer, as "
"well. Once all products have been scanned, validate the transfer to proceed "
"with the stock moves."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/barcode/operations/receipts_deliveries.rst:84
msgid ""
"From this screen, an overview of all receipts to process within that "
"transfer (**WH/IN/000XX**) is shown. At the bottom of the screen, there are "
"options to :guilabel:`Add Product` or :guilabel:`Validate`, depending on "
"whether products need to be added to the operation, or if the whole "
"operation should be validated at once."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/barcode/operations/receipts_deliveries.rst:None
#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/barcode/operations/transfers_scratch.rst:None
msgid "Overview of receipts in transfer to scan."
msgstr "Vue d'ensemble des réceptions dans le transfert à scanner."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/barcode/operations/receipts_deliveries.rst:92
msgid ""
"To process and scan each product individually, scan a product or product "
"packaging, or choose a specific product line. Click the :guilabel:`+#` "
"button (for example, `+10`) to indicate receipt of that product."
msgstr ""
"Pour traiter et scanner chaque produit individuellement, scanner un produit "
"ou un conditionnement de produit, ou choisir une ligne de produit "
"spécifique. Cliquer sur le bouton :guilabel:`+#` (par exemple, `+10`) pour "
"indiquer la réception de ce produit."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/barcode/operations/receipts_deliveries.rst:97
#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/barcode/operations/receipts_deliveries.rst:171
msgid "Editing a product line"
msgstr "Édition d'une ligne de produit"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/barcode/operations/receipts_deliveries.rst:99
msgid ""
"To manually adjust received quantities for a product, click the :icon:`fa-"
"pencil` :guilabel:`(pencil)` icon to open a new screen to edit that product "
"line."
msgstr ""
"Pour ajuster manuellement les quantités reçues pour un produit, cliquer sur "
"l'icône :icon:`fa-pencil` :guilabel:`(crayon)` pour ouvrir un nouvel écran "
"permettant de modifier cette ligne de produit."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/barcode/operations/receipts_deliveries.rst:102
msgid ""
"On this screen, the product that's being received is listed. Under the "
"product name, edit the :guilabel:`Quantity` line. Change the `0` in the line "
"to the desired quantity, or click the :guilabel:`/# Units` button (for "
"example, `/12 Units`) to automatically fill the quantity ordered from the |"
"PO|."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/barcode/operations/receipts_deliveries.rst:107
msgid ""
"Additionally, click the :guilabel:`+1` and :guilabel:`-1` buttons to add or "
"subtract quantity of the product. Click the :guilabel:`+# Units` button to "
"add a product packaging. Click the number keys to add quantity."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/barcode/operations/receipts_deliveries.rst:111
msgid ""
"Below the number keys is the :guilabel:`Location` line, which reads `WH/"
"Stock` by default, unless another *location* is listed on the product "
"itself. Click this line to reveal a drop-down menu of additional locations "
"to choose from."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/barcode/operations/receipts_deliveries.rst:115
#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/barcode/operations/receipts_deliveries.rst:192
msgid ""
"When ready, click :guilabel:`Confirm` to confirm the changes made to the "
"product line."
msgstr ""
"Une fois prêt, cliquer sur :guilabel:`Confirmer` pour confirmer les "
"modifications apportées à la ligne de produit."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/barcode/operations/receipts_deliveries.rst:118
msgid ""
"In the reception operation `WH/IN/00012`, `12 Units` of `Soda Can` are "
"expected to be received. Warehouse employees can scan the barcode of the "
"`Soda Can` product to receive one unit, or because they can be purchased in "
"6-pack packaging, they can scan the packaging barcode. Alternatively, they "
"can click the :icon:`fa-pencil` :guilabel:`(pencil)` icon to manually enter "
"the received quantities."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/barcode/operations/receipts_deliveries.rst:0
#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/barcode/operations/transfers_scratch.rst:0
msgid "Product line editor for individual transfer in Barcode app."
msgstr ""
"Éditeur de ligne de produit pour transfert individuel dans l'application "
