":ref:`Configuration de transporteur tiers <inventory/shipping/third_party>`"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration.rst:16
msgid ""
"`Odoo Tutorials: Delivery Prices <https://www.odoo.com/slides/slide/delivery-"
