msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration.rst:43
msgid "Go to :menuselection:`Inventory app --> Configuration --> Settings`."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration.rst:44
msgid ""
"Scroll to the :guilabel:`Shipping` section and enable "
"the :guilabel:`Delivery Methods` feature by checking the corresponding "
"checkbox."
msgstr ""
"Faire défiler jusqu'à la section :guilabel:`Expédition` et activer la "
"fonctionnalité :guilabel:`Méthodes de livraison` en cochant la case "
"correspondante."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration.rst:0
msgid ""
"Enable the *Delivery Methods* feature by checking the box in Configuration > "
"Settings."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration.rst:50
msgid ""
"On the :guilabel:`Shipping Methods` page, add a method by "
"clicking :guilabel:`New`. Doing so opens a form to provide details about the "
"shipping provider, including:"
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration.rst:53
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Shipping Method` (*Required field*): the name of the delivery "
"method (e.g. `flat-rate shipping`, `same day delivery`, etc.)."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration.rst:55
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Provider` (*Required field*): choose the delivery service, like "
"Fedex, if using a :ref:`third-party carrier <inventory/shipping/"
"third_party>`. Ensure the integration with the shipping carrier is properly "
"installed and select the provider from the drop-down menu."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration.rst:59
msgid ""
"For more details on configuring custom shipping methods, such as :ref:`fixed "
"price <inventory/shipping/fixed>`, :ref:`based on rules <inventory/shipping/"
"rules>`, or :ref:`pickup in store <inventory/shipping/pickup>` options, "
"refer to their respective sections below."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration.rst:62
#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/invoicing.rst:46
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Website`: configure shipping methods for an e-commerce page. "
"Select the applicable website from the drop-down menu, or leave it blank to "
"apply the method to all web pages."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Site Web` : configurer les méthodes d'expédition pour une page e-"
"commerce. Sélectionner le site web applicable dans le menu déroulant, ou "
"laisser vide pour appliquer la méthode à toutes les pages web."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration.rst:64
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Company`: If the shipping method should apply to a specific "
"company, select it from the drop-down menu. Leave the field blank to apply "
"the method to all companies."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration.rst:66
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Routes`: select the applicable route(s) to define different "
"delivery methods, such as standard or express shipping, based on varying "
"lead times. For more information, jump to the :ref:`Set routes on shipping "
"method <inventory/shipping_receiving/shipping-route>` section."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration.rst:72
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Delivery Product` (*Required field*): the product listed on "
"the :ref:`sales order line <inventory/shipping/sales-order>` as the delivery "
"charge."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Produit de livraison` (*Champ obligatoire*) : le produit listé "
"sur la :ref:`ligne de commande client <inventory/shipping/sales-order>` "
"comme frais de livraison."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration.rst:74
#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/invoicing.rst:51
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Free if order amount is above`: checking this box enables free "
"shipping if the customer spends above the specified amount."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Gratuit si le montant de la commande dépasse` : cocher cette case "
"active la livraison gratuite si le client dépense au-delà du montant "
"spécifié."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration.rst:77
msgid ""
"For examples on how to configure specific shipping methods, refer to the "
"sections below."
msgstr ""
"Pour des exemples de configuration de méthodes de livraison spécifiques, se "
"référer aux sections ci-dessous."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration.rst:82
msgid "Fixed price"
msgstr "Prix fixe"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration.rst:84
msgid ""
"To configure a shipping price that is the same for all orders, go "
"to :menuselection:`Inventory app --> Configuration --> Shipping Methods`. "
"Then, click :guilabel:`New`, and on the shipping method form, set "
"the :guilabel:`Provider` to the :guilabel:`Fixed Price` option. Selecting "
"this option makes the :guilabel:`Fixed Price` field become available, which "
"is where the fixed rate shipping amount is defined."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration.rst:90
msgid ""
"To enable free shipping if the amount of the order exceeds a specified "
"amount, check the box :guilabel:`Free if order amount is above` and fill in "
"the amount."
msgstr ""
"Pour activer la livraison gratuite si le montant de la commande dépasse un "
"montant spécifié, cocher la case :guilabel:`Gratuit si le montant de la "
"commande dépasse` et remplir le montant."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration.rst:94
msgid ""
"To set up `$20` flat-rate shipping that becomes free if the customer spends "
"over `$100`, fill in the following fields:"
msgstr ""
"Pour configurer une livraison à tarif fixe de `20 $` qui devient gratuite si "
"le client dépense plus de `100 $`, remplir les champs suivants :"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration.rst:97
msgid ":guilabel:`Shipping Method`: `Flat-rate shipping`"
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration.rst:98
msgid ":guilabel:`Provider`: :guilabel:`Fixed Price`"
msgstr ":guilabel:`Fournisseur` : :guilabel:`Prix fixe`"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration.rst:99
msgid ":guilabel:`Fixed Price`: `$20.00`"
msgstr ":guilabel:`Prix fixe` : `20,00 $`"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration.rst:100
msgid ":guilabel:`Free if order amount is above`: `$100.00`"
msgstr ":guilabel:`Gratuit si le montant de la commande dépasse` : `100,00 $`"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration.rst:101
msgid ":guilabel:`Delivery Product`: `[SHIP] Flat`"
msgstr ":guilabel:`Produit de livraison` : `[SHIP] Flat`"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration.rst:0
msgid "Example of filling out a shipping method."
msgstr "Exemple de remplissage d'une méthode de livraison."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration.rst:109
msgid "Based on rules"
msgstr "Basé sur des règles"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration.rst:111
msgid ""
"To calculate the price of shipping based on pricing rules, set "
"the :guilabel:`Provider` field to the :guilabel:`Based on Rules` option. "
"Optionally, adjust :guilabel:`Margin on Rate` and :guilabel:`Additional "
"margin` to include additional shipping costs."
msgstr ""
"Pour calculer le prix de la livraison en fonction des règles de "
"tarification, définir le champ :guilabel:`Provider` sur "
"l'option :guilabel:`Based on Rules`. Facultativement, "
"ajuster :guilabel:`Margin on Rate` et :guilabel:`Additional margin` pour "
"inclure des frais de livraison supplémentaires."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration.rst:116
msgid "Create pricing rules"
msgstr "Créer des règles de tarification"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration.rst:118
msgid ""
"Navigate to the :guilabel:`Pricing` tab and click :guilabel:`Add a line`. "
"Doing so opens the :guilabel:`Create Pricing Rules` window, where "
"the :guilabel:`Condition` related to the product weight, volume, price, or "
"quantity is compared to a defined amount to calculate "
"the :guilabel:`Delivery Cost`."
msgstr ""
"Accéder à l'onglet :guilabel:`Pricing` et cliquer sur :guilabel:`Add a "
"line`. Cela ouvre la fenêtre :guilabel:`Create Pricing Rules`, où "
"la :guilabel:`Condition` liée au poids, volume, prix ou quantité du produit "
"est comparée à un montant défini pour calculer le :guilabel:`Delivery Cost`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration.rst:123
msgid ""
"Once finished, click either :guilabel:`Save & New` to add another rule, "
"or :guilabel:`Save & Close`."
msgstr ""
"Une fois terminé, cliquer soit sur :guilabel:`Save & New` pour ajouter une "
"autre règle, soit sur :guilabel:`Save & Close`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration.rst:126
msgid ""
"To charge customers $20 in shipping for orders with five or fewer products, "
"set the :guilabel:`Condition` to `Quantity <= 5.00`, and "
"the :guilabel:`Delivery Cost` to `$20`."
msgstr ""
"Pour facturer aux clients 20 $ de frais de livraison pour les commandes "
"contenant cinq produits ou moins, définir la :guilabel:`Condition` sur "
"`Quantity <= 5.00`, et le :guilabel:`Delivery Cost` sur `$20`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration.rst:0
msgid ""
"Display window to add a pricing rule. Set a condition and delivery cost."
msgstr ""
"Fenêtre d'affichage pour ajouter une règle de tarification. Définir une "
"condition et un coût de livraison."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration.rst:132
msgid ""
"To restrict shipping to specific destinations on the eCommerce website, in "
"the shipping method form, navigate to the :guilabel:`Destination "
"Availability` tab and define the :guilabel:`Countries`, :guilabel:`States`, "
"and :guilabel:`Zip Prefixes`. Leave these fields empty if all locations "
"apply."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration.rst:137
msgid "Calculate delivery cost"
msgstr "Calculer le coût de livraison"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration.rst:139
msgid ""
"Shipping cost is the :guilabel:`Delivery cost` specified in the rule that "
"satisfies the :guilabel:`Condition`, plus any extra charges from "
"the :guilabel:`Margin on rate` and :guilabel:`Additional margin`."
msgstr ""
"Le coût de livraison est le :guilabel:`Delivery cost` spécifié dans la règle "
"qui satisfait la :guilabel:`Condition`, plus les frais supplémentaires de "
"la :guilabel:`Margin on rate` et de la :guilabel:`Additional margin`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration.rst:143
msgid ""
"Total = Rule's~Delivery~Cost + (Margin~on~rate \\times Rule's~Delivery~Cost) "
"+ Additional~margin\n"
"\n"
msgstr ""
"Total = Rule's~Delivery~Cost + (Margin~on~rate \\times Rule's~Delivery~Cost) "
"+ Additional~margin\n"
"\n"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration.rst:147
msgid "With the two following rules set up:"
msgstr "Avec les deux règles suivantes configurées :"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration.rst:149
msgid "If the order contains five or fewer products, shipping is $20"
msgstr ""
"Si la commande contient cinq produits ou moins, la livraison est de 20 $"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration.rst:150
msgid "If the order contains more than five products, shipping is $50."
msgstr ""
"Si la commande contient plus de cinq produits, la livraison est de 50 $."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration.rst:152
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Margin on Rate` is `10%` and :guilabel:`Additional margin` is "
"`$9.00`."
msgstr ""
"La :guilabel:`Margin on Rate` est de `10%` et la :guilabel:`Additional "
"margin` est de `$9.00`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration.rst:None
msgid ""
