"After completing the setup, get the Bpost account ID and passphrase, by "
"navigating to the :guilabel:`Shipping Manager` menu item."
msgstr ""
"Après avoir terminé la configuration, obtenir l'identifiant de compte et la "
"phrase secrète bpost, en accédant à l'élément de menu :guilabel:`Shipping "
"Manager`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/bpost.rst:40
msgid ""
"On the :guilabel:`Shipping Manager` page, go to the :guilabel:`Admin` tab, "
"then the :guilabel:`General Settings` tab, to find the :guilabel:`Account "
"ID` and :guilabel:`Passphrase` needed to configure Odoo's shipping method."
msgstr ""
"Sur la page :guilabel:`Shipping Manager`, aller dans "
"l'onglet :guilabel:`Admin`, puis dans l'onglet :guilabel:`General Settings`, "
"pour trouver l':guilabel:`Account ID` et la :guilabel:`Passphrase` "
"nécessaires pour configurer le mode d'expédition d'Odoo."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/bpost.rst:None
