"haut du formulaire pour publier, activer le mode production ou activer la "
"journalisation de débogage."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/dhl_credentials.rst:127
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Unpublished`/:guilabel:`Published`: Determines if this shipping "
"method is available on the user's **eCommerce** website."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Non publié`/:guilabel:`Publié` : Détermine si ce mode de "
"livraison est disponible sur le site **eCommerce** de l'utilisateur."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/dhl_credentials.rst:130
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Test Environment`/:guilabel:`Production Environment`: Determines "
"whether label creation is for testing and canceled immediately (Test) or "
"generates a real shipping label that is charged to the DHL account "
"(Production)."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Environnement de test`/:guilabel:`Environnement de production` : "
"Détermine si la création d'étiquette est destinée aux tests et annulée "
"immédiatement (Test) ou génère une véritable étiquette d'expédition facturée "
"au compte DHL (Production)."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/dhl_credentials.rst:133
msgid ""
":guilabel:`No Debug`/:guilabel:`Debug Requests`: Determines whether API "
"requests and responses are logged in Odoo (turn on :ref:`developer mode "
"<developer-mode>` and go to :menuselection:`Settings app --> Technical --> "
"Logging`)."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Pas de débogage`/:guilabel:`Déboguer les requêtes` : Détermine si "
"les requêtes et réponses API sont enregistrées dans Odoo (activer "
"le :ref:`mode développeur <developer-mode>` et aller "
"dans :menuselection:`Application Paramètres --> Technique --> "
"Journalisation`)."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/easypost.rst:3
msgid "EasyPost integration"
msgstr "Intégration EasyPost"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/easypost.rst:5
msgid ""
"Set up the EasyPost shipping connector in Odoo to manage EasyPost shipments "
"to clients directly within Odoo."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/easypost.rst:8
msgid ""
"EasyPost is a service that allows users to connect with multiple carriers, "
"like UPS, USPS, FedEx, DHL, and more. Odoo can then connect to EasyPost to "
"purchase labels from those carriers."
msgstr ""
"EasyPost est un service qui permet aux utilisateurs de se connecter à "
"plusieurs transporteurs, comme UPS, USPS, FedEx, DHL, et d'autres. Odoo peut "
"ensuite se connecter à EasyPost pour acheter des étiquettes auprès de ces "
"transporteurs."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/easypost.rst:11
#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/shiprocket.rst:9
msgid "To configure it, complete these steps:"
msgstr "Pour le configurer, compléter ces étapes :"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/easypost.rst:13
msgid ""
":ref:`Create an EasyPost account <inventory/shipping_receiving/easypost-"
"account>`."
msgstr ""
":ref:`Créer un compte EasyPost <inventory/shipping_receiving/easypost-"
"account>`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/easypost.rst:14
msgid ""
":ref:`Integrate carrier accounts if the carrier is not enabled on the "
"EasyPost account <inventory/shipping_receiving/integrate-easypost-carrier>`."
msgstr ""
":ref:`Intégrer les comptes transporteur si le transporteur n'est pas activé "
"sur le compte EasyPost <inventory/shipping_receiving/integrate-easypost-"
"carrier>`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/easypost.rst:16
msgid ""
":ref:`Obtain Test and Production API keys <inventory/shipping_receiving/"
"easypost-api-keys>`."
msgstr ""
":ref:`Obtenir les clés API de test et de production <inventory/"
"shipping_receiving/easypost-api-keys>`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/easypost.rst:17
msgid ""
":ref:`Set up the shipping method in Odoo <inventory/shipping_receiving/"
"easypost-method>`."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/easypost.rst:19
msgid ""
"Upon completion, it is possible to calculate shipping costs based on package "
"size and weight, have the charges applied directly to an EasyPost business "
"account, and automatically print EasyPost tracking labels in Odoo."
msgstr ""
"Une fois terminé, il est possible de calculer les frais de port en fonction "
"de la taille et du poids du colis, de faire appliquer les frais directement "
"sur un compte professionnel EasyPost, et d'imprimer automatiquement les "
"étiquettes de suivi EasyPost dans Odoo."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/easypost.rst:28
msgid ""
"To begin, go to the `EasyPost <https://www.easypost.com>`__ website to "
"create or log into the company's EasyPost business account."
msgstr ""
"Pour commencer, aller sur le site `EasyPost <https://www.easypost.com>`__ "
"pour créer ou se connecter au compte professionnel EasyPost de l'entreprise."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/easypost.rst:31
msgid ""
"Follow the website's steps to complete registration and sign up for shipping "
"services. Some shipping services (like USPS and DHL Express) are "
"automatically enabled."
msgstr ""
"Suivre les étapes du site pour compléter l'inscription et s'inscrire aux "
"services d'expédition. Certains services d'expédition (comme USPS et DHL "
"Express) sont automatiquement activés."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/easypost.rst:37
msgid "Integrating other carrier accounts"
msgstr "Intégrer d'autres comptes transporteur"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/easypost.rst:39
msgid ""
"To use a different carrier, it is possible to `enable Wallet Carrier "
"Accounts <https://support.easypost.com/hc/en-us/articles/21336276718605-"
"Enabling-Wallet-Carriers-Using-the-EasyPost-Dashboard>`__ to purchase labels "
"from EasyPost. Alternatively, if a user has their own carrier account, they "
"can `enable it on EasyPost <https://support.easypost.com/hc/en-us/articles/"
"25246240687373-Bring-Your-Own-Carrier-Account-to-EasyPost>`__. Then, after "
"these accounts are enabled, Odoo can integrate with the EasyPost account and "
"manage labels."
msgstr ""
"Pour utiliser un autre transporteur, il est possible d'`activer les comptes "
"transporteur Wallet <https://support.easypost.com/hc/en-us/articles/"
"21336276718605-Enabling-Wallet-Carriers-Using-the-EasyPost-Dashboard>`__ "
"pour acheter des étiquettes auprès d'EasyPost. Alternativement, si un "
"utilisateur possède son propre compte transporteur, il peut l'`activer sur "
"EasyPost <https://support.easypost.com/hc/en-us/articles/25246240687373-"
"Bring-Your-Own-Carrier-Account-to-EasyPost>`__. Ensuite, une fois ces "
"comptes activés, Odoo peut s'intégrer au compte EasyPost et gérer les "
"étiquettes."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/easypost.rst:50
msgid "Obtain Test and Production API keys"
msgstr "Obtenir les clés API de test et de production"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/easypost.rst:52
msgid ""
"After completing the setup, create Test and Production API keys. On the "
"EasyPost website, click the :guilabel:`Account Settings` link, then open "
"the :guilabel:`API Keys` page."
msgstr ""
"Après avoir terminé la configuration, créer les clés API de test et de "
"production. Sur le site Web d'EasyPost, cliquer sur le "
"lien :guilabel:`Account Settings`, puis ouvrir la page :guilabel:`API Keys`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/easypost.rst:55
msgid ""
"If these API keys have not yet been created, click :guilabel:`Add Additional "
"API Key`. Select either :guilabel:`Production` or :guilabel:`Test`. The API "
"key is automatically created. Follow the same process to create both keys."
msgstr ""
"Si ces clés API n'ont pas encore été créées, cliquer sur :guilabel:`Add "
"Additional API Key`. Sélectionner :guilabel:`Production` "
"ou :guilabel:`Test`. La clé API est automatiquement créée. Suivre le même "
"processus pour créer les deux clés."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/easypost.rst:None
msgid "Create API keys on the EasyPost API Keys page."
msgstr "Créer les clés API sur la page API Keys d'EasyPost."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/easypost.rst:67
msgid ""
"With those necessary credentials, configure the EasyPost shipping method in "
"Odoo by going to :menuselection:`Inventory app --> Configuration --> "
"Shipping Methods`."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/easypost.rst:70
msgid "On the *Shipping Methods* page, click :guilabel:`New`."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/easypost.rst:72
msgid ""
"In the :guilabel:`Provider` field, select :guilabel:`Easypost` from the drop-"
"down menu. Doing so reveals the *Easypost Configuration* tab at the bottom "
"of the form, where the EasyPost API keys should be entered."
msgstr ""
"Dans le champ :guilabel:`Fournisseur`, sélectionner :guilabel:`Easypost` "
"dans le menu déroulant. Cela fait apparaître l'onglet *Configuration "
"Easypost* en bas du formulaire, où les clés API EasyPost doivent être "
"saisies."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/easypost.rst:76
msgid ""
"For details on configuring the other fields on the shipping method, such "
"as :guilabel:`Delivery Product`, refer to the :ref:`Delivery method "
"<inventory/shipping_receiving/shipping-methods-details>` documentation."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/easypost.rst:81
msgid ""
"To generate EasyPost shipping labels through Odoo, ensure "
"the :guilabel:`Integration Level` option is set to :guilabel:`Get Rate and "
"Create Shipment`."
msgstr ""
"Pour générer des étiquettes d'expédition EasyPost via Odoo, s'assurer que "
"l'option :guilabel:`Niveau d'intégration` est définie sur :guilabel:`Get "
"Rate and Create Shipment`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/easypost.rst:84
msgid "In the *Easypost Configuration* tab, complete the following fields:"
msgstr ""
"Dans l'onglet *Configuration Easypost*, compléter les champs suivants :"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/easypost.rst:86
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Test API Key`: the Test API key in the EasyPost Account Settings."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Clé API de test` : la clé API de test dans les paramètres du "
"compte EasyPost."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/easypost.rst:87
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Production API Key`: the Production API key in the EasyPost "
"Account Settings."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Clé API de production` : la clé API de production dans les "
"paramètres du compte EasyPost."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/easypost.rst:88
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Label Format`: "
"Choose :guilabel:`PNG`, :guilabel:`PDF`, :guilabel:`ZPL`, "
"or :guilabel:`EPL2` from the drop-down menu."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Format d'étiquette` : "
"choisir :guilabel:`PNG`, :guilabel:`PDF`, :guilabel:`ZPL` "
"ou :guilabel:`EPL2` dans le menu déroulant."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/easypost.rst:90
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Generate Return Label`: Select to automatically generate a return "
"label when validating the delivery."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Générer une étiquette de retour` : sélectionner pour générer "
"automatiquement une étiquette de retour lors de la validation de la "
"livraison."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/easypost.rst:93
msgid ""
"Save the shipping method by clicking the :icon:`fa-cloud-"
"upload` :guilabel:`(Save manually)` icon."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/easypost.rst:95
msgid ""
"Click the :guilabel:`Load your Easypost carrier accounts` link under the API "
"keys."
msgstr ""
"Cliquer sur le lien :guilabel:`Load your Easypost carrier accounts` sous les "
"clés API."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/easypost.rst:None
msgid "Load the Easypost carrier accounts into Odoo."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/easypost.rst:100
msgid ""
"The *Select a carrier* pop-up window opens. Select a shipping carrier from "
"the drop-down menu, then click :guilabel:`Select`."
msgstr ""
"La fenêtre contextuelle *Sélectionner un transporteur* s'ouvre. Sélectionner "
"un transporteur dans le menu déroulant, puis cliquer "
"sur :guilabel:`Sélectionner`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/easypost.rst:103
msgid ""
"After the carrier type has been selected, complete the :guilabel:`Default "
"Package Type` and :guilabel:`Default Service Level` fields."
msgstr ""
"Une fois le type de transporteur sélectionné, compléter les "
"champs :guilabel:`Type de colis par défaut` et :guilabel:`Niveau de service "
"par défaut`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/easypost.rst:None
msgid ""
"Select a package type and service level that should be used for the carrier."
msgstr ""
"Sélectionner un type de colis et un niveau de service à utiliser pour le "
"transporteur."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/easypost.rst:110
msgid "Turn on the Easypost integration"
msgstr "Activer l'intégration Easypost"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/easypost.rst:112
msgid ""
"After the EasyPost connection is set up, use the smart buttons at the top of "
"the form to publish, turn on production mode, or activate debug logging."
msgstr ""
"Une fois la connexion EasyPost configurée, utiliser les boutons intelligents "
"en haut du formulaire pour publier, activer le mode production ou activer la "
"journalisation de débogage."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/easypost.rst:115
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Unpublished/Published`: determines if this shipping method is "
"available on the user's **eCommerce** website."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/easypost.rst:117
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Test Environment/Production Environment`: determines whether "
"label creation is for testing and cancelled immediately (Test) or generating "
"a real shipping label that is charged to the EasyPost account (Production)."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Environnement de test/Environnement de production` : détermine si "
"la création d'étiquette est destinée aux tests et annulée immédiatement "
"(Test) ou génère une véritable étiquette d'expédition facturée au compte "
"EasyPost (Production)."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/easypost.rst:120
msgid ""
":guilabel:`No Debug/Debug Requests`: determines whether API requests and "
"responses are logged in Odoo (turn on **developer mode** and go "
"to :menuselection:`Settings app --> Technical --> Logging`)."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Pas de débogage/Déboguer les requêtes` : détermine si les "
"requêtes et réponses API sont enregistrées dans Odoo (activer le **mode "
"développeur** et aller dans :menuselection:`application Paramètres --> "
"Technique --> Journalisation`)."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/fedex.rst:3
msgid "FedEx integration"
msgstr "Intégration FedEx"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/fedex.rst:5
msgid ""
"Integrating a FedEx account with Odoo's **Inventory** app makes it possible "
"to :doc:`calculate shipping rates <../setup_configuration>` "
"and :doc:`generate shipping labels <labels>` within Odoo. This is "
"accomplished by enabling the FedEx *shipping connector*, then configuring at "
"least one *shipping method*."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/fedex.rst:11
msgid ""
"As of October 21, 2025, the FedEx integration using the latest API is "
"temporarily unavailable while Odoo finalizes its solution-provider "
"validation for FedEx. New setups are currently blocked, and existing "
"integrations using the FedEx Shipping (Legacy) provider will stop working as "
"of June 1, 2026."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/fedex.rst:16
msgid ""
"For a temporary solution, the :doc:`Sendcloud integration "
"<sendcloud_shipping>` also supports FedEx services. To request further "
"assistance, `submit a support ticket <https://www.odoo.com/help>`_."
msgstr ""
"Pour une solution temporaire, l':doc:`intégration Sendcloud "
"<sendcloud_shipping>` prend également en charge les services FedEx. Pour "
"demander une assistance supplémentaire, `soumettre un ticket de support "
"<https://www.odoo.com/help>`_."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/fedex.rst:21
msgid ""
"This documentation contains configuration details specific to FedEx "
"integration. See the documentation on :doc:`third-party shippers "
"<third_party_shipper>` for general shipper integration instructions."
msgstr ""
"Cette documentation contient des détails de configuration spécifiques à "
"l'intégration FedEx. Consultez la documentation sur les :doc:`expéditeurs "
"tiers <third_party_shipper>` pour les instructions générales d'intégration "
"des expéditeurs."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/fedex.rst:26
#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/usps.rst:12
msgid "Enable shipping connector"
msgstr "Activer le connecteur d'expédition"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/fedex.rst:28
msgid ""
"To enable the shipping connector for FedEx, open the :menuselection:`Apps` "
"app. Search for `FedEx`. :guilabel:`Activate` the shipping connector."
msgstr ""
"Pour activer le connecteur d'expédition pour FedEx, ouvrir "
"l'application :menuselection:`Apps`. Rechercher `FedEx`. :guilabel:`Activer` "
"le connecteur d'expédition."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/fedex.rst:32
#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/shiprocket.rst:94
#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/usps.rst:48
msgid "Configure shipping method"
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/fedex.rst:34
msgid ""
"After the FedEx shipping connector is enabled, it is necessary to configure "
"at least one shipping method. After doing so, the shipping method can be "
"included in sales orders (SOs), and used to compute shipping costs, and "
"print shipping labels."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/fedex.rst:38
msgid ""
"To see all shipping methods for every shipper with a connector enabled, "
"navigate to :menuselection:`Inventory app --> Configuration --> Shipping "
"Methods`."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/fedex.rst:41
msgid ""
"Select a FedEx shipping method to open its form. Alternatively, "
"click :guilabel:`New` to open a blank form, and configure a new shipping "
"method."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/fedex.rst:None
msgid "The form for a FedEx shipping method."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/fedex.rst:50
msgid ""
"At the very top of a shipping method form are fields used to configure the "
"way the method operates in Odoo. In the :guilabel:`Provider` field, "
"select :guilabel:`FedEx` from the drop-down menu, if it is not already "
"selected."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/fedex.rst:54
msgid ""
"The rest of the fields in this section are general to all shipping "
"providers. For details on how to fill them out, see the documentation "
"on :doc:`third-party shippers <third_party_shipper>`."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/fedex.rst:58
msgid "FedEx Configuration tab"
msgstr "Onglet Configuration FedEx"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/fedex.rst:60
msgid ""
"The options in the *Fedex Configuration* tab of a FedEx shipping method form "
"are used to connect the method to a FedEx account, and configure the "
"shipping details associated with the method (drop-off type, package type, "
"etc.)."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/fedex.rst:64
msgid ""
"A FedEx business account is required to obtain the information needed to "
"fill out the fields in this tab. To create a new account, navigate to "
"FedEx's `Open Account <https://www.fedex.com/en-us/open-account.html>`_ "
"page, click on :guilabel:`Create Account`, and follow the instructions."
msgstr ""
"Un compte professionnel FedEx est nécessaire pour obtenir les informations "
"requises pour remplir les champs de cet onglet. Pour créer un nouveau "
"compte, accéder à la page FedEx `Ouvrir un compte <https://www.fedex.com/en-"
"us/open-account.html>`_, cliquer sur :guilabel:`Créer un compte` et suivre "
"les instructions."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/fedex.rst:69
msgid ""
"Then, register the FedEx account in the database. Click "
"the :guilabel:`Register FedEx Account` button. The *FedEx Account "
"Registration* window opens. Accept the end user license agreement (EULA) by "
"selecting the :guilabel:`I acknowledge the reading of the FedEx End User "
"License Agreement` and :guilabel:`I accept the terms of FedEx EULA to start "
"shipping` checkboxes, then click :guilabel:`Accept and Continue`."
msgstr ""
"Ensuite, enregistrer le compte FedEx dans la base de données. Cliquer sur le "
"bouton :guilabel:`Enregistrer un compte FedEx`. La fenêtre *Enregistrement "
"du compte FedEx* s'ouvre. Accepter le contrat de licence utilisateur final "
"(CLUF) en cochant les cases :guilabel:`Je reconnais avoir lu le Contrat de "
"Licence Utilisateur Final FedEx` et :guilabel:`J'accepte les conditions du "
"CLUF FedEx pour commencer l'expédition`, puis cliquer "
"sur :guilabel:`Accepter et continuer`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/fedex.rst:75
msgid ""
"In the *FedEx Account Registration - Shipper Information* window, enter "
"the :guilabel:`FedEx Account Number`. Enter the name of the company in "
"the :guilabel:`Customer Name` field and provide the business address. If "
"products are being shipped from a residential address, select "
"the :guilabel:`Residential Address` checkbox. Click the :guilabel:`Validate "
"Address` button."
msgstr ""
"Dans la fenêtre *Enregistrement du compte FedEx - Informations sur "
"l'expéditeur*, saisir le :guilabel:`Numéro de compte FedEx`. Saisir le nom "
"de l'entreprise dans le champ :guilabel:`Nom du client` et fournir l'adresse "
"professionnelle. Si les produits sont expédiés depuis une adresse "
"résidentielle, cocher la case :guilabel:`Adresse résidentielle`. Cliquer sur "
"le bouton :guilabel:`Valider l'adresse`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/fedex.rst:80
msgid ""
"Next, choose a :guilabel:`Validation Option` to verify access to the "
"account. This is a form of multi-factor authentication (MFA). Two options "
"are available:"
msgstr ""
"Ensuite, choisir une :guilabel:`Option de validation` pour vérifier l'accès "
"au compte. Il s'agit d'une forme d'authentification multifacteur (AMF). Deux "
"options sont disponibles :"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/fedex.rst:83
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Invoice Validation`: Use information from a recent invoice "
"(within the past 90 days) to validate the account information."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Validation de facture` : utiliser les informations d'une facture "
"récente (datant de moins de 90 jours) pour valider les informations du "
"compte."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/fedex.rst:85
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Secure Code Validation`: Receive a PIN "
"via :guilabel:`Email`, :guilabel:`SMS`, or :guilabel:`Voice Call`."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Validation par code sécurisé` : recevoir un code PIN "
"par :guilabel:`E-mail`, :guilabel:`SMS` ou :guilabel:`Appel vocal`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/fedex.rst:88
msgid ""
"If successful, the *FedEx Account Registration - Success* window displays, "
"and the account is available for all companies. To change this setting, "
"click :guilabel:`Open FedEx Account Form` and modify the company settings."
msgstr ""
"En cas de succès, la fenêtre *Enregistrement du compte FedEx - Succès* "
"s'affiche et le compte est disponible pour toutes les sociétés. Pour "
"modifier ce paramètre, cliquer sur :guilabel:`Ouvrir le formulaire de compte "
"FedEx` et modifier les paramètres de la société."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/fedex.rst:92
msgid ""
"In the *FedEx Configuration* tab, provide more information about the "
"shipping method:"
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/fedex.rst:94
msgid ""
":guilabel:`FedEx Service Type`: Select the FedEx service used to ship a "
"package."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Type de service FedEx` : sélectionner le service FedEx utilisé "
"pour expédier un colis."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/fedex.rst:95
msgid ""
":guilabel:`FedEx Drop-Off Type`: Select the method for getting a package "
"into FedEx's possession."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Type de dépôt FedEx` : sélectionner la méthode pour remettre un "
"colis à FedEx."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/fedex.rst:96
msgid ""
":guilabel:`FedEx Package Type`: Select the type of package used for the "
"shipping method."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Type de colis FedEx` : sélectionner le type de colis utilisé pour "
"la méthode d'expédition."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/fedex.rst:97
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Package Weight Unit`: Select the unit of measure used to weigh "
"packages."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Unité de poids du colis` : sélectionner l'unité de mesure "
"utilisée pour peser les colis."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/fedex.rst:98
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Package Length Unit`: This field changes based on what is "
"selected in the :guilabel:`Package Weight Unit` field. If :guilabel:`Pounds` "
"is selected, the length unit updates to :guilabel:`Inches`. "
"If :guilabel:`Kilograms` is selected, the length unit updates "
"to :guilabel:`Centimeters`."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Unité de longueur du colis` : ce champ change en fonction de ce "
"qui est sélectionné dans le champ :guilabel:`Unité de poids du colis`. "
"Si :guilabel:`Livres` est sélectionné, l'unité de longueur "
"devient :guilabel:`Pouces`. Si :guilabel:`Kilogrammes` est sélectionné, "
"l'unité de longueur devient :guilabel:`Centimètres`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/fedex.rst:102
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Label Size`: Select the type of shipping label used for packages."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/fedex.rst:103
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Label Format`: Select the file format used by Odoo to generate "
"shipping labels."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Format d'étiquette` : sélectionner le format de fichier utilisé "
"par Odoo pour générer les étiquettes d'expédition."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/fedex.rst:106
msgid ""
"The options that should be selected on the *FedEx Configuration* tab of a "
"shipping method depend on the negotiated shipping services of the associated "
"FedEx account. To confirm the available services for a FedEx account, visit "
"the *Account Management* page after logging in to the FedEx website or speak "
"with a customer service representative."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/fedex.rst:112
msgid "Options section"
msgstr "Section options"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/fedex.rst:114
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`Options` section of the *FedEx Configuration* tab provides a "
"few additional options to further configure the shipping method:"
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/fedex.rst:117
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Generate Return Label`: Select this checkbox to automatically "
"generate a label when a delivery is validated."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Générer une étiquette de retour` : Cocher cette case pour générer "
"automatiquement une étiquette lors de la validation d'une livraison."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/fedex.rst:119
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Email Notifications`: Select this checkbox to send updates via "
"email to customers, if an email address is configured for the customer."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Notifications par e-mail` : Cocher cette case pour envoyer des "
"mises à jour par e-mail aux clients, si une adresse e-mail est configurée "
"pour le client."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/fedex.rst:121
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Duties paid by`: Use the drop-down menu to select whether duty "
"charges should be paid by the :guilabel:`Sender` or :guilabel:`Recipient`."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Droits payés par` : Utiliser le menu déroulant pour sélectionner "
"si les frais de douane doivent être payés par l':guilabel:`Expéditeur` ou "
"le :guilabel:`Destinataire`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/fedex.rst:123
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Residential delivery`: Specify when to mark a recipient's address "
"as residential."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Livraison résidentielle` : Spécifier quand marquer l'adresse d'un "
"destinataire comme résidentielle."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/fedex.rst:124
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Generate invoice`: Specify whether an invoice should be generated "
"as a PDF or sent as an electronic trade document. This is typically required "
"when commercial invoices are needed for international shipments."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Générer une facture` : Spécifier si une facture doit être générée "
"en PDF ou envoyée comme document commercial électronique. Ceci est "
"généralement requis lorsque des factures commerciales sont nécessaires pour "
"les expéditions internationales."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/fedex.rst:129
msgid "Declared Value section"
msgstr "Section Valeur déclarée"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/fedex.rst:131
msgid ""
"Specify the :guilabel:`Declared Value Percentage` for insurance purposes."
msgstr ""
"Spécifier le :guilabel:`Pourcentage de la valeur déclarée` à des fins "
"d'assurance."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/fedex.rst:134
msgid "Activate shipping method"
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/fedex.rst:136
msgid ""
"By default, shipping methods in Odoo are created within a *test "
"environment*. This means they can only be used for testing purposes, and are "
"unable to generate actual shipping orders."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/fedex.rst:139
msgid ""
"To activate a shipping method in a *production environment*, click "
"the :icon:`fa-stop` :guilabel:`Test Environment` smart button at the top of "
"the shipping method form. After doing so, the smart buttons changes to "
"read :icon:`fa-play` :guilabel:`Production Environment`."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/fedex.rst:143
msgid ""
"With the production environment enabled, validating a delivery order using "
"the shipping method generates an actual shipping label with FedEx."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/fedex.rst:146
msgid ""
"Click the :icon:`fa-play` :guilabel:`Production Environment` smart button to "
"return the shipping method to a test environment."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/fedex.rst:150
msgid ""
"**Do not** enable the production environment for a shipping method before it "
"is ready to be used for actual shipping orders. Doing so may lead to the "
"creation of unwanted charges with FedEx."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/invoicing.rst:3
msgid "Shipping cost invoicing"
msgstr "Facturation des frais de livraison"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/invoicing.rst:5
msgid ""
"Invoicing customers for shipping after delivery ensures accurate charges "
"based on real-time shipping factors like distance, weight, and method."
msgstr ""
"Facturer les clients pour l'expédition après la livraison garantit des frais "
"précis basés sur des facteurs d'expédition en temps réel tels que la "
"distance, le poids et la méthode."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/invoicing.rst:8
msgid "In Odoo, shipping costs can be invoiced in two ways:"
msgstr ""
"Dans Odoo, les frais de livraison peuvent être facturés de deux manières :"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/invoicing.rst:10
msgid ""
"Agree with the customer on a fixed cost and :ref:`include it in the sale "
"order. <inventory/shipping/invoice-so>`"
msgstr ""
"Convenir avec le client d'un coût fixe et :ref:`l'inclure dans la commande "
"client. <inventory/shipping/invoice-so>`"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/invoicing.rst:13
msgid ""
":ref:`Invoice shipping costs to the customer post-delivery <inventory/"
"shipping/invoice-shipping>`, reflecting the actual expenses incurred by the "
"business."
msgstr ""
":ref:`Facturer les frais de livraison au client après la livraison "
"<inventory/shipping/invoice-shipping>`, reflétant les dépenses réelles "
"engagées par l'entreprise."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/invoicing.rst:19
msgid ""
"To set prices to delivery methods, go to :menuselection:`Inventory app --> "
"Configuration --> Settings`. Under the :guilabel:`Shipping` section, enable "
"the :guilabel:`Delivery Methods` feature. Then, click :guilabel:`Save`."
msgstr ""
"Pour définir les prix des méthodes de livraison, aller "
"à :menuselection:`Application Inventaire --> Configuration --> Paramètres`. "
"Dans la section :guilabel:`Expédition`, activer la "
"fonctionnalité :guilabel:`Méthodes de livraison`. Ensuite, cliquer "
"sur :guilabel:`Enregistrer`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/invoicing.rst:None
msgid "Enable the \"Delivery Methods\" feature in Settings."
msgstr ""
"Activer la fonctionnalité « Méthodes de livraison » dans les paramètres."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/invoicing.rst:30
msgid ""
"Next, configure the the price of each delivery method by going "
"to :menuselection:`Inventory app --> Configuration --> Shipping Methods` and "
"click the :guilabel:`Create` button. Doing so opens a form to provide "
"details about the shipping provider, including:"
msgstr ""
"Ensuite, configurer le prix de chaque méthode de livraison en allant "
"dans :menuselection:`Application Inventaire --> Configuration --> Méthodes "
"d'expédition` et cliquer sur le bouton :guilabel:`Créer`. Cela ouvre un "
"formulaire pour fournir des détails sur le prestataire d'expédition, "
"notamment :"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/invoicing.rst:34
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Shipping Method` (*required*) the name of the delivery method "
"(e.g. `flat-rate shipping`, `same day delivery`, etc.)."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Méthode d'expédition` (*requis*) : le nom de la méthode de "
"livraison (par exemple `expédition à tarif fixe`, `livraison le jour même`, "
"etc.)."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/invoicing.rst:36
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Provider` (*required*): choose the delivery service, like FedEx, "
"if using a third-party carrier Ensure the integration with the shipping "
"carrier is properly installed and select the provider from the drop-down "
"menu."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Prestataire` (*requis*) : choisir le service de livraison, comme "
"FedEx, si un transporteur tiers est utilisé. S'assurer que l'intégration "
"avec le transporteur est correctement installée et sélectionner le "
"prestataire dans le menu déroulant."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/invoicing.rst:41
#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/invoicing.rst:122
#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/labels.rst:27
msgid ":doc:`../setup_configuration/third_party_shipper`"
msgstr ":doc:`../setup_configuration/third_party_shipper`"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/invoicing.rst:43
#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/third_party_shipper.rst:131
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Company`: if the shipping method should apply to a specific "
"company, select it from the drop-down menu. Leave the field blank to apply "
"the method to all companies."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Société` : si la méthode d'expédition doit s'appliquer à une "
"société spécifique, la sélectionner dans le menu déroulant. Laisser le champ "
"vide pour appliquer la méthode à toutes les sociétés."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/invoicing.rst:49
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Delivery Product` (*required*): the product listed on "
"the :ref:`sales order line <inventory/shipping/invoice-on-so>` as the "
"delivery charge."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Article de livraison` (*requis*) : l'article affiché sur "
"la :ref:`ligne de commande client <inventory/shipping/invoice-on-so>` comme "
"frais de livraison."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/invoicing.rst:57
msgid "Invoice cost on sales order"
msgstr "Facturer le coût sur la commande client"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/invoicing.rst:59
msgid ""
"To invoice shipping costs on the sales order, before the item is delivered, "
"go to the :menuselection:`Sales app` and select the desired sales order."
msgstr ""
"Pour facturer les frais d'expédition sur la commande client, avant que "
"l'article ne soit livré, aller dans l':menuselection:`Application Ventes` et "
"sélectionner la commande client souhaitée."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/invoicing.rst:62
msgid ""
"On the sales order, click the :guilabel:`Add Shipping` button at the bottom-"
"right corner."
msgstr ""
"Sur la commande client, cliquer sur le bouton :guilabel:`Ajouter "
"l'expédition` en bas à droite."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/invoicing.rst:None
msgid "Click \"Add Shipping\" button at the bottom right, near the total."
msgstr ""
"Cliquer sur le bouton « Ajouter l'expédition » en bas à droite, près du "
"total."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/invoicing.rst:68
msgid ""
"In the :guilabel:`Add a shipping method` pop-up window, choose the intended "
"carrier in the :guilabel:`Shipping Method` field."
msgstr ""
"Dans la fenêtre contextuelle :guilabel:`Ajouter une méthode d'expédition`, "
"choisir le transporteur souhaité dans le champ :guilabel:`Méthode "
"d'expédition`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/invoicing.rst:71
msgid ""
"Then, click the :guilabel:`Get Rate` button to the calculate shipping price "
"based on real-time shipping data Odoo's shipping carrier integration."
msgstr ""
"Ensuite, cliquer sur le bouton :guilabel:`Obtenir le tarif` pour calculer le "
"prix d'expédition basé sur les données d'expédition en temps réel de "
"l'intégration du transporteur d'Odoo."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/invoicing.rst:74
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`Cost` is automatically calculated using the weight of the "
"items in the order. Finally, click the :guilabel:`Add` button to close the "
"window."
msgstr ""
"Le :guilabel:`Coût` est automatiquement calculé en utilisant le poids des "
"articles dans la commande. Enfin, cliquer sur le bouton :guilabel:`Ajouter` "
"pour fermer la fenêtre."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/invoicing.rst:None
msgid "Calculate shipping by selecting a shipping method."
msgstr "Calculer l'expédition en sélectionnant une méthode d'expédition."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/invoicing.rst:83
msgid ""
"On the sales order, the delivery product appears in the :guilabel:`Order "
"Lines` tab, with the :guilabel:`Unit Price` set as the shipping cost "
"calculated in the :guilabel:`Add a shipping method` pop-up window."
msgstr ""
"Sur la commande client, l'article de livraison apparaît dans "
"l'onglet :guilabel:`Lignes de commande`, avec le :guilabel:`Prix unitaire` "
"défini comme le coût d'expédition calculé dans la fenêtre "
"contextuelle :guilabel:`Ajouter une méthode d'expédition`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/invoicing.rst:None
msgid "Show delivery product on the sales order line."
msgstr "Afficher l'article de livraison sur la ligne de commande client."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/invoicing.rst:91
msgid ""
"Finally, after the product is delivered, click the :guilabel:`Create "
"invoice` button, and an invoice is created that includes the shipping cost "
"that was added earlier."
msgstr ""
"Enfin, après la livraison du produit, cliquer sur le bouton :guilabel:`Créer "
"une facture`, et une facture est créée qui inclut le coût d'expédition "
"ajouté précédemment."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/invoicing.rst:None
msgid "Show \"Create Invoice\" button."
msgstr "Afficher le bouton \"Créer une facture\"."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/invoicing.rst:98
msgid ""
"Then, click the :guilabel:`Create and View Invoice` button, and a draft "
"invoice is generated, with the shipping cost included in "
"the :guilabel:`Invoice Lines` tab."
msgstr ""
"Ensuite, cliquer sur le bouton :guilabel:`Créer et afficher la facture`. Une "
"facture brouillon est générée avec les frais d'expédition inclus dans "
"l'onglet :guilabel:`Lignes de facture`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/invoicing.rst:None
msgid "Show delivery product in the invoice line."
msgstr "Afficher le produit de livraison dans la ligne de facture."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/invoicing.rst:108
msgid "Invoice real shipping costs"
msgstr "Facturer les frais d'expédition réels"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/invoicing.rst:110
msgid ""
"To modify the invoice to reflect the real cost of shipping, follow the "
"steps :ref:`above <inventory/shipping/invoice-so>` to create an invoice with "
"a delivery product with a :guilabel:`Unit Price` of zero."
msgstr ""
"Pour modifier la facture afin de refléter le coût réel de l'expédition, "
"suivre les étapes :ref:`ci-dessus <inventory/shipping/invoice-so>` pour "
"créer une facture avec un produit de livraison dont le :guilabel:`Prix "
"unitaire` est zéro."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/invoicing.rst:114
msgid ""
"Then, on a draft invoice, modify the :guilabel:`Unit Price` to reflect the "
"real shipping cost. Finally, invoice the customer the adjusted shipping cost "
"by clicking :guilabel:`Confirm`."
msgstr ""
"Ensuite, sur une facture brouillon, modifier le :guilabel:`Prix unitaire` "
"pour refléter le coût d'expédition réel. Enfin, facturer au client le coût "
"d'expédition ajusté en cliquant sur :guilabel:`Confirmer`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/invoicing.rst:None
msgid "Show delivery product on the invoice line."
msgstr "Afficher le produit de livraison sur la ligne de facture."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/invoicing.rst:123
msgid ":doc:`../setup_configuration/labels`"
msgstr ":doc:`../setup_configuration/labels`"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/label_type.rst:3
msgid "Change shipping label size"
msgstr "Changer la taille de l'étiquette d'expédition"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/label_type.rst:8
msgid ""
"In Odoo, there are a variety of different types of shipping labels that can "
"be selected for delivery orders. Depending on the types of shipping packages "
"used, different label sizes may be more appropriate, and can be configured "
"to fit the package."
msgstr ""
"Dans Odoo, il existe une variété de types d'étiquettes d'expédition qui "
"peuvent être sélectionnés pour les bons de livraison. Selon les types de "
"colis d'expédition utilisés, différentes tailles d'étiquettes peuvent être "
"plus appropriées et peuvent être configurées pour s'adapter au colis."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/label_type.rst:15
msgid ""
"In the :menuselection:`Inventory` module, go "
"to :menuselection:`Configuration --> Delivery --> Shipping Methods.` Click "
"on a delivery method to choose it. For the following example, *FedEx "
"International* will be used."
msgstr ""
"Dans le module :menuselection:`Inventaire`, allez "
"à :menuselection:`Configuration --> Livraison --> Modes d'expédition.` "
"Cliquez sur un mode de livraison pour en choisir un. Dans l'exemple suivant, "
"nous utilisons *FedEx International*."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/label_type.rst:None
msgid "Different shipping methods."
msgstr "Différents modes d'expédition."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/label_type.rst:23
msgid ""
"In the :guilabel:`Configuration` tab, under :guilabel:`Label Type`, choose "
"one of the label types available. The availability varies depending on the "
"carrier."
msgstr ""
"Dans l'onglet :guilabel:`Configuration`, dans :guilabel:`Type d'étiquette`, "
"choisissez l'un des types d'étiquette disponibles. La disponibilité varie en "
"fonction du transporteur."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/label_type.rst:None
msgid "Select a label type."
msgstr "Sélectionnez un type d'étiquette."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/label_type.rst:30
msgid ""
"When a sales order with the corresponding shipping company is confirmed and "
"a delivery order is validated, the shipping label will be automatically "
"created as a PDF and appear in the :guilabel:`Chatter`."
msgstr ""
"Lorsqu'une commande avec le transporteur correspondant est confirmée et un "
"bon de livraison est validé, l'étiquette d'expédition sera automatiquement "
"créée en tant que PDF et apparaîtra dans le :guilabel:`Chatter`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/label_type.rst:37
msgid ""
"In the :menuselection:`Sales` application, click :guilabel:`Create` and "
"select an international customer. Click :guilabel:`Add A Product` and select "
"an item. Click :guilabel:`Add Shipping`, select a shipping method, then "
"click :guilabel:`Get Rate`, and finally, click :guilabel:`Add`."
msgstr ""
"Dans l'application :menuselection:`Ventes`, cliquez sur :guilabel:`Créer` et "
"sélectionnez un client international. Cliquez sur :guilabel:`Ajouter un "
"produit` et sélectionnez un article. Cliquez sur :guilabel:`Ajouter "
"l'expédition`, sélectionnez un mode d'expédition, puis cliquez "
"sur :guilabel:`Calculer le tarif` et enfin cliquez sur :guilabel:`Ajouter`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/label_type.rst:None
msgid "Add a shipping method and rate to a sales order."
msgstr "Ajouter un mode d'expédition et un tarif à une commande"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/label_type.rst:45
msgid ""
"Once the quotation is confirmed by clicking :guilabel:`Confirm`, "
"a :guilabel:`Delivery` smart button will appear."
msgstr ""
"Une fois que le devis est confirmé en cliquant sur :guilabel:`Confirmer`, un "
"bouton intelligent :guilabel:`Livraison` apparaîtra."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/label_type.rst:None
msgid "Delivery order smart button."
msgstr "Bouton intelligent bon de livraison."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/label_type.rst:52
msgid ""
"Once the delivery order is validated by clicking :guilabel:`Validate` in the "
"delivery order, the shipping documents appear in the :guilabel:`Chatter`."
msgstr ""
"Une fois que le bon de livraison est validé en cliquant "
"sur :guilabel:`Valider` sur le bon de livraison, les documents d'expédition "
"apparaîtront dans le :guilabel:`Chatter`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/label_type.rst:None
msgid "Shipping PDF documents."
msgstr "Documents d'expédition en PDF."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/label_type.rst:60
msgid "Example labels"
msgstr "Exemples d'étiquettes"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/label_type.rst:62
msgid ""
"The default :guilabel:`Label Type` is :guilabel:`Paper Letter`. An example "
"of a FedEx letter sized label is:"
msgstr ""
"Le :guilabel:`Type d'étiquette` par défaut est :guilabel:`Paper Letter`. "
"Voici un exemple d'étiquette FedEx au format lettre :"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/label_type.rst:None
msgid "Full page letter size FedEx shipping label."
msgstr "Étiquette d'expédition FedEx pleine page au format lettre."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/label_type.rst:69
msgid "For comparison, an example of a FedEx bottom-half label is:"
msgstr ""
"À titre de comparaison, voici un exemple d'étiquette FedEx de la moitié "
"inférieure :"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/label_type.rst:None
msgid "Half page letter size FedEx shipping label."
msgstr "Une demi-page d'étiquette d'expédition FedEx au format lettre."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/labels.rst:3
msgid "Print shipping labels"
msgstr "Imprimer les étiquettes d'expédition"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/labels.rst:8
msgid ""
"Integrate Odoo with :doc:`third-party shipping carriers <../"
"setup_configuration/third_party_shipper>` to automatically generate shipping "
"labels that includes prices, destination addresses, tracking numbers, and "
"barcodes."
msgstr ""
"Intégrer Odoo avec des :doc:`transporteurs tiers <../setup_configuration/"
"third_party_shipper>` pour générer automatiquement des étiquettes "
"d'expédition incluant les prix, adresses de destination, numéros de suivi et "
"codes-barres."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/labels.rst:13
msgid ""
":ref:`Automatically print shipping carrier labels <inventory/"
"shipping_receiving/carrier-labels>`"
msgstr ""
":ref:`Imprimer automatiquement les étiquettes des transporteurs <inventory/"
"shipping_receiving/carrier-labels>`"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/labels.rst:18
msgid ""
"To generate labels for a third-party shipping carrier, first :doc:`install "
"the third-party shipping connector <../setup_configuration/"
"third_party_shipper>`. Then, configure and activate the :ref:`delivery "
"method <inventory/shipping_receiving/configure-delivery-method>`, being sure "
"to set the :guilabel:`Integration Level` to :guilabel:`Get Rate and Create "
"Shipment` to generate shipping labels. Finally, provide the "
"company's :ref:`source address <inventory/shipping_receiving/configure-"
"source-address>` and :ref:`product weights <inventory/shipping_receiving/"
"configure-weight>`."
msgstr ""
"Pour générer des étiquettes pour un transporteur tiers, "
"d'abord :doc:`installer le connecteur de transporteur tiers <../"
"setup_configuration/third_party_shipper>`. Ensuite, configurer et activer "
"le :ref:`mode de livraison <inventory/shipping_receiving/configure-delivery-"
"method>`, en veillant à définir le :guilabel:`Niveau d'intégration` "
"sur :guilabel:`Obtenir le tarif et créer l'expédition` pour générer les "
"étiquettes d'expédition. Enfin, fournir l':ref:`adresse source <inventory/"
"shipping_receiving/configure-source-address>` de l'entreprise et "
"les :ref:`poids des produits <inventory/shipping_receiving/configure-"
"weight>`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/labels.rst:None
msgid "Set the \"Get Rate and Create Shipment\" option."
msgstr "Définir l'option \"Obtenir le tarif et créer l'expédition\"."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/labels.rst:36
msgid "Labels for multi-step"
msgstr "Étiquettes pour multi-étapes"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/labels.rst:38
msgid ""
"For companies using :doc:`two <../daily_operations/"
"receipts_delivery_two_steps>` or :doc:`three step delivery <../"
"daily_operations/delivery_three_steps>`, labels can be triggered to print "
"after validating the picking or packing operation. To do that, go "
"to :menuselection:`Inventory app --> Configuration --> Operations Types`, "
"and choose the desired operation."
msgstr ""
"Pour les entreprises utilisant une livraison en :doc:`deux <../"
"daily_operations/receipts_delivery_two_steps>` ou :doc:`trois étapes <../"
"daily_operations/delivery_three_steps>`, les étiquettes peuvent être "
"déclenchées pour impression après validation de l'opération de préparation "
"ou d'emballage. Pour ce faire, aller dans :menuselection:`Application "
"Inventaire --> Configuration --> Types d'opérations`, et choisir l'opération "
"souhaitée."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/labels.rst:43
msgid ""
"On the :guilabel:`Operation Type` configuration page, tick "
"the :guilabel:`Print Label` checkbox. Enabling this feature ensures that the "
"third-party shipping label is printed upon validating this operation."
msgstr ""
"Sur la page de configuration du :guilabel:`Type d'opération`, cocher la "
"case :guilabel:`Imprimer l'étiquette`. Activer cette fonctionnalité garantit "
"que l'étiquette du transporteur tiers est imprimée lors de la validation de "
"cette opération."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/labels.rst:48
msgid ""
"For :doc:`two-step delivery <../daily_operations/"
"receipts_delivery_two_steps>`, where products are placed directly in "
"packages during picking, companies can print shipping labels during picking "
"instead of delivery. Odoo allows users to enable the :guilabel:`Print Label` "
"feature on the `Pick` operation itself to achieve this flexibility."
msgstr ""
"Pour la :doc:`livraison en deux étapes <../daily_operations/"
"receipts_delivery_two_steps>`, où les produits sont placés directement dans "
"des colis pendant la préparation, les entreprises peuvent imprimer les "
"étiquettes d'expédition pendant la préparation plutôt qu'à la livraison. "
"Odoo permet aux utilisateurs d'activer la fonctionnalité :guilabel:`Imprimer "
"l'étiquette` sur l'opération de préparation elle-même pour obtenir cette "
"flexibilité."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/labels.rst:0
msgid "Enable the \"Print Label\" feature."
msgstr "Activer la fonctionnalité \"Imprimer l'étiquette\"."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/labels.rst:58
msgid "Print tracking labels"
msgstr "Imprimer les étiquettes de suivi"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/labels.rst:60
msgid ""
"Tracking labels are printed when specific operations are validated. By "
"default, validating a delivery order (DO) generates a tracking label in the "
"chatter."
msgstr ""
"Les étiquettes de suivi sont imprimées lorsque des opérations spécifiques "
"sont validées. Par défaut, la validation d'un bon de livraison génère une "
"étiquette de suivi dans le fil de discussion."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/labels.rst:64
msgid ""
"For companies using two or three step delivery, refer to the :ref:`printing "
"labels for multi-step delivery <inventory/shipping_receiving/picking-"
"config>` section to learn how to print the label after validating a picking "
"or packing operation."
msgstr ""
"Pour les entreprises utilisant une livraison en deux ou trois étapes, se "
"référer à la section :ref:`imprimer des étiquettes pour une livraison multi-"
"étapes <inventory/shipping_receiving/picking-config>` pour apprendre comment "
"imprimer l'étiquette après avoir validé une opération de préparation ou "
"d'emballage."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/labels.rst:68
msgid ""
"When both the *Sales* and *Inventory* apps are installed, begin in "
"the :menuselection:`Sales` app, and proceed to the desired quotation or "
"sales order (SO). There, and :ref:`add the shipping cost <inventory/"
"shipping_receiving/add-shipping-quote>` to the order. Then, navigate to the "
"linked |DO| — or another operation type when using multi-step delivery — to "
"validate the operation and print the label."
msgstr ""
"Lorsque les applications *Ventes* et *Inventaire* sont installées, commencer "
"dans l'application :menuselection:`Ventes`, et accéder au devis ou à la "
"commande client souhaitée. Ensuite, :ref:`ajouter les frais de livraison "
"<inventory/shipping_receiving/add-shipping-quote>` à la commande. Puis, "
"accéder au |DO| lié — ou à un autre type d'opération lors de l'utilisation "
"d'une livraison multi-étapes — pour valider l'opération et imprimer "
"l'étiquette."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/labels.rst:74
msgid ""
"If only the *Inventory* app is installed, create :abbr:`DOs (Delivery "
"Orders)` directly in the :menuselection:`Inventory` app, :ref:`add the third-"
"party carrier <inventory/shipping_receiving/validate-print-label>` in "
"the :guilabel:`Carrier` field, and validate the |DO|."
msgstr ""
"Si seule l'application *Inventaire* est installée, créer des :abbr:`BL (Bons "
"de Livraison)` directement dans "
"l'application :menuselection:`Inventaire`, :ref:`ajouter le transporteur "
"tiers <inventory/shipping_receiving/validate-print-label>` dans le "
"champ :guilabel:`Transporteur`, et valider le |DO|."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/labels.rst:82
msgid "Add shipping on quotation"
msgstr "Ajouter la livraison sur le devis"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/labels.rst:84
msgid ""
"To generate a tracking label for an order, begin by creating a quotation "
"in :menuselection:`Sales app --> Orders --> Quotations`, "
"clicking :guilabel:`New`, and filling out the quotation form. Then, click "
"the :guilabel:`Add Shipping` button in the bottom-right corner of the "
"quotation."
msgstr ""
"Pour générer une étiquette de suivi pour une commande, commencer par créer "
"un devis dans :menuselection:`application Ventes --> Commandes --> Devis`, "
"cliquer sur :guilabel:`Nouveau`, et remplir le formulaire de devis. Ensuite, "
"cliquer sur le bouton :guilabel:`Ajouter la livraison` dans le coin "
"inférieur droit du devis."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/labels.rst:None
msgid "Show the \"Add Shipping\" button on the quotation."
msgstr "Afficher le bouton \"Ajouter la livraison\" sur le devis."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/labels.rst:92
msgid ""
"In the resulting pop-up window, select the intended carrier from "
"the :guilabel:`Shipping Method` drop-down menu. The :guilabel:`Total Order "
"Weight` field is automatically populated, based on the :ref:`weight of "
"products in the order <inventory/shipping_receiving/configure-weight>`. "
"Modify this field to overwrite the predicted weight, and use this weight to "
"estimate the cost of shipping."
msgstr ""
"Dans la fenêtre contextuelle qui s'affiche, sélectionner le transporteur "
"souhaité dans le menu déroulant :guilabel:`Mode de livraison`. Le "
"champ :guilabel:`Poids total de la commande` est automatiquement rempli, en "
"fonction du :ref:`poids des produits dans la commande <inventory/"
"shipping_receiving/configure-weight>`. Modifier ce champ pour remplacer le "
"poids prévu, et utiliser ce poids pour estimer le coût de livraison."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/labels.rst:97
msgid ""
"Next, click :guilabel:`Get Rate` to display the shipping cost for the "
"customer, via the third-party carrier in the :guilabel:`Cost` field."
msgstr ""
"Ensuite, cliquer sur :guilabel:`Obtenir le tarif` pour afficher le coût de "
"livraison pour le client, via le transporteur tiers dans le "
"champ :guilabel:`Coût`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/labels.rst:101
msgid ""
"If clicking :guilabel:`Get Rate` results in an error, ensure "
"the :ref:`warehouse's address <inventory/shipping_receiving/configure-source-"
"address>` and :ref:`weight of products in the order <inventory/"
"shipping_receiving/configure-weight>` are properly configured."
msgstr ""
"Si cliquer sur :guilabel:`Obtenir le tarif` entraîne une erreur, s'assurer "
"que :ref:`l'adresse de l'entrepôt <inventory/shipping_receiving/configure-"
"source-address>` et le :ref:`poids des produits dans la commande <inventory/"
"shipping_receiving/configure-weight>` sont correctement configurés."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/labels.rst:105
msgid ""
"Click :guilabel:`Add` to add the cost to the quotation, which is listed as "
"the :ref:`configured delivery product <inventory/shipping_receiving/delivery-"
"product>`. Finally, click :guilabel:`Confirm` on the quotation, and click "
"the :guilabel:`Delivery` smart button to access the |DO|."
msgstr ""
"Cliquer sur :guilabel:`Ajouter` pour ajouter le coût au devis, qui est "
"répertorié comme le :ref:`produit de livraison configuré <inventory/"
"shipping_receiving/delivery-product>`. Enfin, cliquer "
"sur :guilabel:`Confirmer` sur le devis, et cliquer sur le bouton "
"intelligent :guilabel:`Livraison` pour accéder au |DO|."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/labels.rst:None
msgid "Show \"Get rate\" pop-up window."
msgstr "Afficher la fenêtre contextuelle \"Obtenir le tarif\"."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/labels.rst:115
msgid ""
"For users who do not have the *Sales* app installed, specify "
"the :guilabel:`Carrier` by going to the :menuselection:`Inventory` app, "
"navigating to the |DO|, and going to the :guilabel:`Additional Info` tab."
msgstr ""
"Pour les utilisateurs qui n'ont pas l'application *Ventes* installée, "
"spécifier le :guilabel:`Transporteur` en allant dans "
"l'application :menuselection:`Inventaire`, en accédant au |DO|, et en allant "
"dans l'onglet :guilabel:`Informations supplémentaires`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/labels.rst:0
msgid "Show the \"Additional Info\" tab of a delivery order."
msgstr ""
"Afficher l'onglet \"Informations supplémentaires\" d'un bon de livraison."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/labels.rst:126
msgid "Validate delivery order"
msgstr "Valider le bon de livraison"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/labels.rst:128
msgid ""
"On a delivery order form, navigate to the :guilabel:`Additional Info` tab to "
"ensure the third-party shipping carrier has been added to "
"the :guilabel:`Carrier` field."
msgstr ""
"Sur un formulaire de bon de livraison, accéder à "
"l'onglet :guilabel:`Informations supplémentaires` pour s'assurer que le "
"transporteur tiers a été ajouté au champ :guilabel:`Transporteur`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/labels.rst:132
msgid ""
"If the *Sales* app is not installed, the third-party carrier is set in "
"the :guilabel:`Carrier` field."
msgstr ""
"Si l'application *Ventes* n'est pas installée, le transporteur tiers est "
"défini dans le champ :guilabel:`Transporteur`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/labels.rst:135
msgid ""
"After the items in the order have been packed, click :guilabel:`Validate` to "
"get the shipping carrier's tracking number, and generate the shipping label."
msgstr ""
"Une fois les articles de la commande emballés, cliquer "
"sur :guilabel:`Valider` pour obtenir le numéro de suivi du transporteur, et "
"générer l'étiquette de livraison."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/labels.rst:139
msgid ""
"Create or select an existing delivery order by going to "
"the :menuselection:`Inventory` app, and selecting the :guilabel:`Delivery "
"Orders` card."
msgstr ""
"Créer ou sélectionner un bon de livraison existant en allant dans "
"l'application :menuselection:`Inventaire`, et en sélectionnant la "
"carte :guilabel:`Bons de livraison`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/labels.rst:142
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`Tracking Reference` number is generated in "
"the :guilabel:`Additional Info` tab of the delivery order. Click "
"the :guilabel:`Tracking` smart button to access the tracking link from the "
"shipping carrier's website."
msgstr ""
"Le numéro de :guilabel:`Référence de suivi` est généré dans "
"l'onglet :guilabel:`Informations supplémentaires` du bon de livraison. "
"Cliquer sur le bouton intelligent :guilabel:`Suivi` pour accéder au lien de "
"suivi depuis le site web du transporteur."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/labels.rst:146
msgid "The tracking label is found in PDF format in the chatter."
msgstr ""
"L'étiquette de suivi se trouve au format PDF dans le fil de discussion."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/labels.rst:None
msgid "Show generated shipping label in the chatter."
msgstr "Afficher l'étiquette d'expédition générée dans le fil de discussion."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/labels.rst:153
msgid ""
"For multi-package shipping, one label is generated per package. Each label "
"appears in the chatter."
msgstr ""
"Pour les expéditions multi-colis, une étiquette est générée par colis. "
"Chaque étiquette apparaît dans le fil de discussion."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/labels.rst:160
msgid "Sample label generated from Odoo's shipping connector with FedEx."
msgstr ""
"Exemple d'étiquette générée depuis le connecteur d'expédition d'Odoo avec "
"FedEx."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/multipack.rst:3
msgid "Multi-package shipments"
msgstr "Expédition de plusieurs colis"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/multipack.rst:5
msgid ""
"In some cases, a delivery order with multiple items may need to be shipped "
"in multiple packages. This may be necessary if the items are too large to "
"ship in a single package, or if certain items cannot be packaged together. "
"Shipping a single delivery order in multiple packages allows each item to be "
"packaged differently, without creating multiple delivery orders."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/multipack.rst:13
msgid ""
"To split a delivery order across multiple packages, the *Packages* setting "
"must be enabled. To do so, navigate to :menuselection:`Inventory app --> "
"Configuration --> Settings`, then in the *Operations* section, select "
"the :guilabel:`Packages` checkbox. Click :guilabel:`Save` to confirm the "
"change."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/multipack.rst:None
msgid "The Packages setting on the Inventory app settings page."
msgstr ""
"Le paramètre Colis sur la page des paramètres de l'application Inventaire."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/multipack.rst:24
msgid "Ship items in multiple packages"
msgstr "Expédier des articles dans plusieurs colis"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/multipack.rst:26
msgid ""
"To split items in the same delivery order across multiple packages, navigate "
"to the :menuselection:`Inventory` app. On the *Inventory Overview* page, "
"click the :guilabel:`# to Process` button on the :guilabel:`Delivery Orders` "
"card. On the *Delivery Orders* page, select a delivery order that has "
"multiple items, multiple quantities of the same item, or both."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/multipack.rst:31
msgid ""
"On the *Operations* tab, select the :icon:`fa-list` :guilabel:`(Open Move)` "
"icon for the product that will be shipped in the first package."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/multipack.rst:None
msgid "The menu icon for a product in a delivery order."
msgstr "L'icône de menu pour un produit dans un bon de livraison."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/multipack.rst:37
msgid ""
"This opens the *Open: Stock move* pop-up window. In the table in the pop-up "
"window, the :guilabel:`Quantity` column shows the total quantity of the "
"product included in the delivery order."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/multipack.rst:40
msgid ""
"If the full quantity will be shipped in the first package, enter "
"the :guilabel:`Demand` value in the :guilabel:`Quantity` column. If less "
"than the full quantity will be shipped in the first package, enter a smaller "
"number than the :guilabel:`Demand` quantity. Then, specify "
"a :guilabel:`Destination Package` for the product."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/multipack.rst:None
msgid "The Detailed Operations pop-up for a product in a delivery order."
msgstr ""
"La fenêtre contextuelle des opérations détaillées pour un produit d'un bon "
"de livraison."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/multipack.rst:48
msgid ""
"If the product is to be split into multiple packages, click "
"the :guilabel:`Add a line` link and split the :guilabel:`Quantity` between "
"the different :guilabel:`Destination Package` options that are created."
msgstr ""
"Si le produit doit être divisé en plusieurs colis, cliquer sur le "
"lien :guilabel:`Ajouter une ligne` et répartir la :guilabel:`Quantité` entre "
"les différentes options :guilabel:`Colis de destination` créées."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/multipack.rst:52
msgid "Click :guilabel:`Save` to confirm the packages and close the pop-up."
msgstr ""
"Cliquer sur :guilabel:`Enregistrer` pour confirmer les colis et fermer la "
"fenêtre contextuelle."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/multipack.rst:54
msgid ""
"If packaging multiple products into the same package, repeat the steps for "
"each product. Be sure to specify the same :guilabel:`Destination Package` in "
"the *Open: Stock move* window."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/multipack.rst:57
msgid ""
"For the next package, follow the same steps outlined above, marking "
"the :guilabel:`Quantity` and :guilabel:`Destination Package` for each item "
"to be included. Continue doing so until the full quantity of all products "
"has been added to packages."
msgstr ""
"Pour le colis suivant, suivre les mêmes étapes décrites ci-dessus, en "
"indiquant la :guilabel:`Quantité` et le :guilabel:`Colis de destination` "
"pour chaque article à inclure. Continuer ainsi jusqu'à ce que la quantité "
"totale de tous les produits ait été ajoutée aux colis."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/multipack.rst:61
msgid ""
"Finally, after all packages have been shipped, click :guilabel:`Validate` to "
"confirm that the delivery order is complete."
msgstr ""
"Enfin, une fois tous les colis expédiés, cliquer sur :guilabel:`Valider` "
"pour confirmer que le bon de livraison est terminé."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/multipack.rst:65
msgid ""
"After one or more packages are created, a :icon:`fa-"
"cubes` :guilabel:`Packages` smart button appears above the delivery order. "
"Click the :icon:`fa-cubes` :guilabel:`Packages` smart button to open the "
"*Packages* page for the delivery order, where each package can be selected "
"to view all of its items."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/multipack.rst:0
msgid "The Packages smart button on a delivery order."
msgstr "Le bouton intelligent Colis sur un bon de livraison."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/multipack.rst:76
msgid "Create a back order for items to be shipped later"
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/multipack.rst:78
msgid ""
"If some items will be shipped later than others, there is no need to package "
"them until they are ready to ship. Instead, create a back order for the "
"items being shipped later."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/multipack.rst:81
msgid ""
"Begin by shipping the items that will be shipped immediately. If they will "
"be shipped in multiple packages, follow the steps in :ref:`inventory/"
"shipping/multiple-packages` to package them as required. If they will be "
"shipped in a single package, mark the :guilabel:`Quantity` "
"and :guilabel:`Destination Package` for all of the products in that shipment."
msgstr ""
"Commencer par expédier les articles qui seront expédiés immédiatement. S'ils "
"seront expédiés dans plusieurs colis, suivre les étapes dans :ref:`inventory/"
"shipping/multiple-packages` pour les emballer selon les besoins. S'ils "
"seront expédiés dans un seul colis, indiquer la :guilabel:`Quantité` et "
"le :guilabel:`Colis de destination` pour tous les produits de cette "
"expédition."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/multipack.rst:86
msgid ""
"After all quantities being shipped immediately are packaged, return to the "
"delivery order form. Change the :guilabel:`Quantity` for the back ordered "
"items to `0` or to the partial quantity being shipped. Then, click "
"the :guilabel:`Validate` button, and a :guilabel:`Create Backorder?` pop-up "
"window appears. Click the :guilabel:`Create Backorder` button. Doing so "
"immediately confirms the items being shipped and creates a new delivery "
"order for the items that will be shipped later."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/multipack.rst:None
msgid "Create a back order."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/multipack.rst:95
msgid ""
"The back order delivery order will be listed in the chatter of the original "
"delivery order, with a message that reads :guilabel:`The backorder WH/OUT/"
"XXXXX has been created`. Click on :guilabel:`WH/OUT/XXXXX` in the message to "
"view the back order delivery order."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/multipack.rst:None
msgid ""
"The back order delivery order listed in the chatter of the original delivery "
"order."
msgstr ""

