msgstr ""
"**Informations client** : lors de la création d'un devis, s'assurer que "
"le :guilabel:`Client` sélectionné dispose d'un numéro de téléphone, d'une "
"adresse e-mail et d'une adresse de livraison valides."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/sendcloud_shipping.rst:215
msgid ""
"To verify, select the :guilabel:`Customer` field to open their contact page. "
"Here, add their shipping address in the :guilabel:`Contact` field, along "
"with their :guilabel:`Mobile` number and :guilabel:`Email` address."
msgstr ""
"Pour vérifier, sélectionner le champ :guilabel:`Client` pour ouvrir sa page "
"de contact. Ici, ajouter son adresse de livraison dans le "
"champ :guilabel:`Contact`, ainsi que son numéro de :guilabel:`Mobile` et son "
"adresse :guilabel:`E-mail`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/sendcloud_shipping.rst:219
msgid ""
"**Product weight**: ensure all products in an order have a "
"specified :guilabel:`Weight` in the :guilabel:`Inventory` tab of their "
"product form. Refer to the :ref:`Product weight section <inventory/"
"shipping_receiving/configure-weight>` of this article for detailed "
"instructions."
msgstr ""
"**Poids du produit** : s'assurer que tous les produits d'une commande ont "
"un :guilabel:`Poids` spécifié dans l'onglet :guilabel:`Inventaire` de leur "
"fiche produit. Consulter la :ref:`section poids du produit <inventory/"
"shipping_receiving/configure-weight>` de cet article pour des instructions "
"détaillées."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/sendcloud_shipping.rst:223
msgid ""
"**Warehouse address**: ensure the warehouse name and address in Odoo match "
"the :ref:`previously defined warehouse <inventory/shipping_receiving/"
"sendcloud-warehouse-config>` in the Sendcloud setup. For details on "
"warehouse configuration in Odoo, refer to the :ref:`warehouse configuration "
"section <inventory/shipping_receiving/configure-source-address>` of the "
"third-party shipping documentation."
msgstr ""
"**Adresse de l'entrepôt** : s'assurer que le nom et l'adresse de l'entrepôt "
"dans Odoo correspondent à l':ref:`entrepôt précédemment défini <inventory/"
"shipping_receiving/sendcloud-warehouse-config>` dans la configuration de "
"Sendcloud. Pour plus de détails sur la configuration de l'entrepôt dans "
"Odoo, consulter la :ref:`section configuration de l'entrepôt <inventory/"
"shipping_receiving/configure-source-address>` de la documentation "
"d'expédition tierce."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/sendcloud_shipping.rst:230
msgid "Generate labels with Sendcloud"
msgstr "Générer des étiquettes avec Sendcloud"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/sendcloud_shipping.rst:232
msgid ""
"When creating a quotation in Odoo, add shipping and a :guilabel:`Sendcloud "
"shipping product`. Then, :guilabel:`Validate` the delivery. Shipping label "
"documents are automatically generated in the chatter, which include the "
"following:"
msgstr ""
"Lors de la création d'un devis dans Odoo, ajoutez l'expédition et "
"un :guilabel:`produit d'expédition Sendcloud`. Ensuite, :guilabel:`validez` "
"la livraison. Les documents d'étiquettes d'expédition sont générés "
"automatiquement dans le chatter, qui comprennent les éléments suivants :"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/sendcloud_shipping.rst:236
#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/starshipit_shipping.rst:205
msgid ":guilabel:`Shipping label(s)` depending on the number of packages."
msgstr ":guilabel:`Étiquette(s) d'expédition` selon le nombre de colis."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/sendcloud_shipping.rst:237
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Return label(s)` if the Sendcloud connector is configured for "
"returns."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Étiquette(s) de retour` si le connecteur Sendcloud est configuré "
"pour les retours."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/sendcloud_shipping.rst:238
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Customs document(s)` should the destination country require them."
msgstr ":guilabel:`Document(s) de douane` si le pays de destination les exige."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/sendcloud_shipping.rst:240
msgid "Additionally, the tracking number is now available."
msgstr "De plus, le numéro de suivi est maintenant disponible."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/sendcloud_shipping.rst:243
msgid ""
"When return labels are created, Sendcloud automatically charges the "
"configured Sendcloud account."
msgstr ""
"Lors de la création d'étiquettes de retour, Sendcloud facture "
"automatiquement le compte Sendcloud configuré."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/sendcloud_shipping.rst:246
msgid "Shipping rules"
msgstr "Règles d'expédition"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/sendcloud_shipping.rst:248
msgid ""
"Optionally, create shipping rules to automatically generate shipping labels "
"tailored to different product needs. For example, a shipping rule can be "
"created for customers shipping expensive jewelry items to purchase insurance."
msgstr ""
"Créer optionnellement des règles d'expédition pour générer automatiquement "
"des étiquettes d'expédition adaptées aux différents besoins des produits. "
"Par exemple, une règle d'expédition peut être créée pour que les clients "
"expédiant des bijoux coûteux souscrivent une assurance."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/sendcloud_shipping.rst:253
msgid ""
"Shipping rules do **not** affect :ref:`shipping rate calculations <inventory/"
"shipping_receiving/third-party-rate>`, and are only used to improve the "
"process of :doc:`generating shipping labels <labels>`."
msgstr ""
"Les règles d'expédition n'affectent **pas** les :ref:`calculs de tarifs "
"d'expédition <inventory/shipping_receiving/third-party-rate>`, et sont "
"uniquement utilisées pour améliorer le processus de :doc:`génération "
"d'étiquettes d'expédition <labels>`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/sendcloud_shipping.rst:257
msgid ""
"To use shipping rules, navigate to :menuselection:`Inventory app --> "
"Configuration --> Delivery: Shipping Methods`, and select the intended "
"`Sendcloud` shipping method."
msgstr ""
"Pour utiliser les règles d'expédition, aller à :menuselection:`Application "
"Inventaire --> Configuration --> Livraison : Méthodes de livraison`, et "
"sélectionner la méthode d'expédition `Sendcloud` souhaitée."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/sendcloud_shipping.rst:260
msgid ""
"Under the :guilabel:`Sendcloud Configuration` tab, in "
"the :guilabel:`OPTIONS` section, choose the kind of shipments the shipping "
"rules apply to, via the :guilabel:`Use Sendcloud shipping rules` field."
msgstr ""
"Sous l'onglet :guilabel:`Configuration Sendcloud`, dans la "
"section :guilabel:`OPTIONS`, choisir le type d'expéditions auxquelles les "
"règles d'expédition s'appliquent, via le champ :guilabel:`Utiliser les "
"règles d'expédition Sendcloud`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/sendcloud_shipping.rst:264
msgid ""
"From here, choose either: :guilabel:`Shipping` to "
"customers, :guilabel:`Returns` from customers, or :guilabel:`Both`."
msgstr ""
"Choisir ensuite : :guilabel:`Expédition` vers les "
"clients, :guilabel:`Retours` des clients, ou :guilabel:`Les deux`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/sendcloud_shipping.rst:None
msgid "Use Shipping Rules field."
msgstr "Champ Utiliser les règles d'expédition."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/sendcloud_shipping.rst:271
msgid ""
"Then, in the Sendcloud website, navigate to :menuselection:`Settings --> "
"Shipping rules`. Create a new shipping rule by clicking :guilabel:`Create "
"New`."
msgstr ""
"Ensuite, sur le site Web de Sendcloud, aller à :menuselection:`Paramètres --"
"> Règles d'expédition`. Créer une nouvelle règle d'expédition en cliquant "
"sur :guilabel:`Créer nouveau`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/sendcloud_shipping.rst:274
msgid ""
"In the :guilabel:`Actions` section, set a :guilabel:`Condition` to determine "
"when the rule applies. Then, configure what to do when packages meet the "
"condition."
msgstr ""
"Dans la section :guilabel:`Actions`, définir une :guilabel:`Condition` pour "
"déterminer quand la règle s'applique. Ensuite, configurer ce qu'il faut "
"faire lorsque les colis remplissent la condition."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/sendcloud_shipping.rst:278
msgid ""
"`Create shipping rules on Sendcloud <https://support.sendcloud.com/hc/en-us/"
"articles/ 10274470454292-How-to-create-shipping-rules#examples-smart-"
"shipping-rules>`_"
msgstr ""
"`Créer des règles d'expédition sur Sendcloud <https://support.sendcloud.com/"
"hc/en-us/articles/ 10274470454292-How-to-create-shipping-rules#examples-"
"smart-shipping-rules>`_"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/sendcloud_shipping.rst:282
msgid "FAQ"
msgstr "FAQ"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/sendcloud_shipping.rst:285
msgid "Shipment is too heavy"
msgstr "L'envoi est trop lourd"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/sendcloud_shipping.rst:287
msgid ""
"If the shipment is too heavy for the Sendcloud service that is configured, "
"then the weight is split to simulate multiple packages. Products will need "
"to be put in different :guilabel:`Packages` to :guilabel:`Validate` the "
"transfer and generate labels."
msgstr ""
"Si l'envoi est trop lourd pour le service Sendcloud configuré, le poids est "
"divisé pour simuler plusieurs colis. Les produits devront être mis en "
"différents :guilabel:`colis` pour :guilabel:`valider` le transfert et "
"générer les étiquettes."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/sendcloud_shipping.rst:291
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Rules` can also be set up in Sendcloud to use other shipping "
"methods when the weight is too heavy. However, note that these rules will "
"not apply to the shipping price calculation on the calculation on the sales "
"order."
msgstr ""
"Il est possible de configurer des :guilabel:`règles` dans Sendcloud pour "
"utiliser d'autres modes d'expédition quand le poids est trop lourd. "
"Cependant, notez que ces règles ne s'appliquent pas au calcul du prix "
"d'expédition sur le calcul du bon de commande."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/sendcloud_shipping.rst:296
msgid "Personal carrier contract"
msgstr "Contrat transporteur personnel"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/sendcloud_shipping.rst:298
msgid ""
"Use custom prices from a direct carrier contract, via CSV upload, by first "
"logging into Sendcloud, navigating to :menuselection:`Settings --> Carriers "
"--> My contracts`, and then selecting the intended contract."
msgstr ""
"Utiliser des tarifs personnalisés issus d'un contrat direct avec un "
"transporteur, via un téléchargement CSV, en se connectant d'abord à "
"Sendcloud, en allant à :menuselection:`Paramètres --> Transporteurs --> Mes "
"contrats`, puis en sélectionnant le contrat souhaité."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/sendcloud_shipping.rst:None
msgid "Navigate to the contracts section in Sendcloud."
msgstr "Aller à la section des contrats dans Sendcloud."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/sendcloud_shipping.rst:306
msgid ""
"Under the :guilabel:`Contract prices` section, click :guilabel:`Download "
"CSV` and fill out the contract prices in the :guilabel:`price` column of the "
"CSV file template."
msgstr ""
"Dans la section :guilabel:`Contract prices`, cliquer sur :guilabel:`Download "
"CSV` et remplir les prix contractuels dans la colonne :guilabel:`price` du "
"fichier CSV modèle."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/sendcloud_shipping.rst:310
msgid ""
"Ensure the CSV file includes the correct prices to avoid any inaccuracies."
msgstr ""
"S'assurer que le fichier CSV contient les prix corrects pour éviter toute "
"inexactitude."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/sendcloud_shipping.rst:None
msgid "Show sample contract CSV from Sendcloud, highlighting the price column."
msgstr ""
"Afficher un exemple de CSV de contrat Sendcloud, en mettant en évidence la "
"colonne price."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/sendcloud_shipping.rst:316
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Upload` the completed CSV file to Sendcloud, then "
"click :guilabel:`Save these prices`."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Télécharger` le fichier CSV complété vers Sendcloud, puis cliquer "
"sur :guilabel:`Save these prices`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/sendcloud_shipping.rst:319
msgid ""
"`Sendcloud: How to upload contract prices with carriers <https://"
"support.sendcloud.com/hc/en-us/articles/5163547066004>`_"
msgstr ""
"`Sendcloud : Comment télécharger les prix contractuels avec les "
"transporteurs <https://support.sendcloud.com/hc/en-us/articles/"
"5163547066004>`_"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/sendcloud_shipping.rst:323
msgid "Measuring volumetric weight"
msgstr "Calcul du poids volumétrique"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/sendcloud_shipping.rst:325
msgid ""
"Many carriers have several measures for weight. There is the actual weight "
"of the products in the parcel, and there is the *volumetric weight* "
"(:dfn:`Volumetric weight is the volume that a package occupies when in "
"transit. In other words it is the physical size of a package`)."
msgstr ""
"De nombreux transporteurs ont plusieurs mesures pour le poids. Il y a le "
"poids réel des produits contenus dans le colis et il y a le *poids "
"volumétrique* (:dfn:`Le poids volumétrique est la place que le colis prend "
"en transit. En d'autres termes, c'est la taille physique d'un colis`)."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/sendcloud_shipping.rst:330
msgid ""
"Check to see if selected carrier(s) already have defined formulas to compute "
"the volumetric weight."
msgstr ""
"Vérifiez si le ou les transporteurs sélectionnés ont déjà défini des "
"formules pour calculer le poids volumétrique."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/sendcloud_shipping.rst:334
msgid ""
"`Sendcloud: How to calculate & automate parcel volumetric weight <https://"
"support.sendcloud.com/ hc/en-us/articles/360059644051-How-to-calculate-"
"automate-parcel-volumetric-weight>`_"
msgstr ""
"`Sendcloud : Comment calculer & automatiser le poids volumétrique d'un colis "
"<https://support.sendcloud.com/ hc/en-us/articles/360059644051-How-to-"
"calculate-automate-parcel-volumetric-weight>`_"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/sendcloud_shipping.rst:338
msgid "Unable to calculate shipping rate"
msgstr "Impossible de calculer les frais d'expédition"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/sendcloud_shipping.rst:340
msgid ""
"First, verify that the product being shipped has a weight that is supported "
"by the selected shipping method. If this is set, then verify that the "
"destination country (from the customer address) is supported by the carrier. "
"The country of origin (warehouse address) should also be supported by the "
"carrier."
msgstr ""
"D'abord, vérifier que le produit à expédier a un poids pris en charge par le "
"mode d'expédition sélectionné. Si c'est le cas, vérifier ensuite que le pays "
"de destination (d'après l'adresse du client) est pris en charge par le "
"transporteur. Le pays d'origine (adresse de l'entrepôt) doit également être "
"pris en charge par le transporteur."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/shiprocket.rst:3
msgid "Shiprocket integration"
msgstr "Intégration Shiprocket"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/shiprocket.rst:5
msgid ""
"Shiprocket is an Indian service that allows users to connect with multiple "
"carriers, like Delhivery, Blue Dart, DTDC, India Post, Xpressbees, and more. "
"To manage Shiprocket shipments to clients directly within Odoo, it must "
"first be configured."
msgstr ""
"Shiprocket est un service indien qui permet aux utilisateurs de se connecter "
"à plusieurs transporteurs, comme Delhivery, Blue Dart, DTDC, India Post, "
"Xpressbees, et plus encore. Pour gérer les expéditions Shiprocket vers les "
"clients directement dans Odoo, il doit d'abord être configuré."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/shiprocket.rst:11
msgid ""
":ref:`Create a Shiprocket account <inventory/shiprocket/account-setup>`."
msgstr ":ref:`Créer un compte Shiprocket <inventory/shiprocket/account-setup>`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/shiprocket.rst:12
msgid ":ref:`Create an API user <inventory/shiprocket/api-user>`."
msgstr ":ref:`Créer un utilisateur API <inventory/shiprocket/api-user>`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/shiprocket.rst:13
msgid ":ref:`Create a sales channel <inventory/shiprocket/sales-channel>`."
msgstr ":ref:`Créer un canal de vente <inventory/shiprocket/sales-channel>`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/shiprocket.rst:14
msgid ":ref:`Enable couriers <inventory/shiprocket/enable-couriers>`."
msgstr ""
":ref:`Activer les transporteurs <inventory/shiprocket/enable-couriers>`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/shiprocket.rst:15
msgid ""
":ref:`Enable the Shiprocket connector in Odoo <inventory/shiprocket/enable>`."
msgstr ""
":ref:`Activer le connecteur Shiprocket dans Odoo <inventory/shiprocket/"
"enable>`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/shiprocket.rst:16
msgid ""
":ref:`Configure the shipping method in Odoo <inventory/shiprocket/"
"configure>`."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/shiprocket.rst:18
msgid ""
"Upon completion, it is possible to calculate shipping costs based on package "
"size and weight, have the charges applied directly to a Shiprocket account, "
"and automatically print Shiprocket tracking labels in Odoo."
msgstr ""
"Une fois terminé, il est possible de calculer les frais d'expédition en "
"fonction de la taille et du poids du colis, de faire appliquer les frais "
"directement sur un compte Shiprocket et d'imprimer automatiquement les "
"étiquettes de suivi Shiprocket dans Odoo."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/shiprocket.rst:27
msgid ""
"To begin, go to the `Shiprocket website <https://app.shiprocket.in/"
"newlogin>`_ to create or log into the company's Shiprocket account."
msgstr ""
"Pour commencer, accéder au `site Web Shiprocket <https://app.shiprocket.in/"
"newlogin>`_ pour créer ou se connecter au compte Shiprocket de l'entreprise."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/shiprocket.rst:30
msgid "Follow the website's steps to complete registration."
msgstr "Suivre les étapes du site Web pour terminer l'inscription."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/shiprocket.rst:35
msgid "Create API user"
msgstr "Créer un utilisateur API"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/shiprocket.rst:37
msgid ""
"On the Shiprocket *Homepage*, open the :menuselection:`Settings` menu. In "
"the *Additional Settings* section, navigate to the :menuselection:`API "
"Users` page."
msgstr ""
"Sur la *page d'accueil* Shiprocket, ouvrir le menu "
":menuselection:`Paramètres`. Dans la section *Paramètres supplémentaires*, "
"accéder à la page :menuselection:`Utilisateurs API`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/shiprocket.rst:40
msgid ""
"On the *API Users* page, click the :guilabel:`+ Add New API User` button. In "
"the *Add New User* window, specify an :guilabel:`Email ID`. Open "
"the :guilabel:`Select Modules to Access` menu and select :guilabel:`Orders "
"(create, "
"update)`, :guilabel:`Settings`, :guilabel:`Shipments`, :guilabel:`Listings`, "
"and :guilabel:`Courier`, then click :guilabel:`Apply`. Finally, "
"click :guilabel:`Create User` to add the user."
msgstr ""
"Sur la page *Utilisateurs API*, cliquer sur le bouton :guilabel:`+ Ajouter "
"un nouvel utilisateur API`. Dans la fenêtre *Ajouter un nouvel utilisateur*, "
"spécifier un :guilabel:`Identifiant e-mail`. Ouvrir le menu "
":guilabel:`Sélectionner les modules à accéder` et sélectionner "
":guilabel:`Commandes (créer, mettre à jour)`, :guilabel:`Paramètres`, "
":guilabel:`Expéditions`, :guilabel:`Annonces` et :guilabel:`Transporteur`, "
"puis cliquer sur :guilabel:`Appliquer`. Enfin, cliquer sur :guilabel:`Créer "
"un utilisateur` pour ajouter l'utilisateur."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/shiprocket.rst:46
msgid "Copy the API password from the *Your API Password* window."
msgstr "Copier le mot de passe API depuis la fenêtre *Votre mot de passe API*."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/shiprocket.rst:None
msgid ""
"Click the Copy token icon to copy the password to the device's clipboard."
msgstr ""
"Cliquer sur l'icône Copier le jeton pour copier le mot de passe dans le "
"presse-papiers de l'appareil."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/shiprocket.rst:54
msgid "Create sales channel"
msgstr "Créer un canal de vente"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/shiprocket.rst:56
msgid ""
"From the sidebar, navigate to :menuselection:`Setup & Manage --> Channels`. "
"On the *Sales Channels* page, click :guilabel:`Connect New Channel`. In the "
"*Shopping Carts* section, click the :guilabel:`Add` button under the "
"*Manual* heading. The *Manual* settings page opens."
msgstr ""
"Depuis la barre latérale, accéder à :menuselection:`Configuration et "
"gestion --> Canaux`. Sur la page *Canaux de vente*, cliquer sur "
":guilabel:`Connecter un nouveau canal`. Dans la section *Paniers d'achat*, "
"cliquer sur le bouton :guilabel:`Ajouter` sous la rubrique *Manuel*. La page "
"de paramètres *Manuel* s'ouvre."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/shiprocket.rst:60
msgid ""
"Specify a :guilabel:`Channel Name`, such as `Odoo`. Click :guilabel:`Save "
"Channel & Test Connection`."
msgstr ""
"Spécifier un :guilabel:`Nom du canal`, tel que `Odoo`. Cliquer sur "
":guilabel:`Enregistrer le canal et tester la connexion`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/shiprocket.rst:None
msgid "Create a sales channel."
msgstr "Créer un canal de vente."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/shiprocket.rst:69
msgid "Configure couriers"
msgstr "Configurer les transporteurs"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/shiprocket.rst:71
msgid ""
"From the sidebar, navigate to :menuselection:`Setup & Manage --> Courier`. "
"On the *Courier Selection* page, enable or disable shipping couriers."
msgstr ""
"Depuis la barre latérale, accéder à :menuselection:`Configuration & "
"Gestion --> Transporteur`. Sur la page *Sélection de transporteur*, activer "
"ou désactiver les transporteurs d'expédition."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/shiprocket.rst:None
msgid "Toggle couriers to select them on the Courier Selection page."
msgstr ""
"Basculer les transporteurs pour les sélectionner sur la page Sélection de "
"transporteur."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/shiprocket.rst:77
msgid ""
"Open the :menuselection:`Courier Priority` page. Set a priority ranking to "
"which orders are assigned and click :guilabel:`Save`. The courier is "
"selected in Odoo based on this priority. For example, "
"if :guilabel:`Cheapest` is selected, the most cost-effective courier is "
"selected."
msgstr ""
"Ouvrir la page :menuselection:`Priorité du transporteur`. Définir un "
"classement de priorité auquel les commandes sont attribuées et cliquer sur "
":guilabel:`Enregistrer`. Le transporteur est sélectionné dans Odoo en "
"fonction de cette priorité. Par exemple, si :guilabel:`Le moins cher` est "
"sélectionné, le transporteur le plus économique est sélectionné."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/shiprocket.rst:84
msgid "Enable connector"
msgstr "Activer le connecteur"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/shiprocket.rst:86
msgid ""
"The *Shiprocket Connector* must be enabled before a shipping method can be "
"configured."
msgstr ""
"Le *Connecteur Shiprocket* doit être activé avant qu'une méthode "
"d'expédition puisse être configurée."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/shiprocket.rst:88
msgid ""
"Navigate to :menuselection:`Inventory app --> Configuration --> Settings`. "
"In the *Shipping Connectors* section, enable :guilabel:`Shiprocket "
"Connector`, then click :guilabel:`Save`."
msgstr ""
"Accéder à :menuselection:`Application Inventaire --> Configuration --> "
"Paramètres`. Dans la section *Connecteurs d'expédition*, activer "
":guilabel:`Connecteur Shiprocket`, puis cliquer sur :guilabel:`Enregistrer`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/shiprocket.rst:96
msgid ""
"Configure the Shiprocket shipping method in Odoo by going "
"to :menuselection:`Inventory app --> Configuration --> Shipping Methods`."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/shiprocket.rst:99
msgid ""
"On the *Shipping Methods* page, open the :guilabel:`ShipRocket Domestic` "
"shipping method, or click :guilabel:`New`."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/shiprocket.rst:102
msgid ""
"In the :guilabel:`Provider` field, select :guilabel:`Shiprocket` from the "
"list of providers. Doing so reveals the *Shiprocket Configuration* tab at "
"the bottom of the form, where Shiprocket credentials are entered."
msgstr ""
"Dans le champ :guilabel:`Fournisseur`, sélectionner :guilabel:`Shiprocket` "
"dans la liste des fournisseurs. Cela fait apparaître l'onglet *Configuration "
"Shiprocket* en bas du formulaire, où les identifiants Shiprocket sont saisis."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/shiprocket.rst:106
msgid ""
"For details on configuring the other fields on the shipping method, such "
"as :guilabel:`Delivery Product`, refer to the :ref:`inventory/"
"setup_configuration/add-method` documentation."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/shiprocket.rst:110
msgid ""
"To generate Shiprocket shipping labels through Odoo, ensure "
"the :guilabel:`Integration Level` option is set to :guilabel:`Get Rate and "
"Create Shipment`."
msgstr ""
"Pour générer des étiquettes d'expédition Shiprocket via Odoo, s'assurer que "
"l'option :guilabel:`Niveau d'intégration` est définie sur :guilabel:`Obtenir "
"le tarif et créer l'expédition`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/shiprocket.rst:114
msgid "Shiprocket Configuration tab"
msgstr "Onglet Configuration Shiprocket"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/shiprocket.rst:116
msgid ""
"Enter the API user email address in the :guilabel:`Shiprocket Email` field. "
"Enter the API password for the user in the :guilabel:`Shiprocket Password` "
"field. Click the :icon:`fa-arrow-right` :guilabel:`Test Connection` link."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/shiprocket.rst:120
msgid ""
"Select :guilabel:`Pickup Request` to send a pickup request when a delivery "
"order is validated."
msgstr ""
"Sélectionner :guilabel:`Demande d'enlèvement` pour envoyer une demande "
"d'enlèvement lorsqu'un bon de livraison est validé."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/shiprocket.rst:122
msgid ""
"Select :guilabel:`Generate Manifest` to generate a shipping manifest and "
"streamline the pickup process."
msgstr ""
"Sélectionner :guilabel:`Générer le manifeste` pour générer un manifeste "
"d'expédition et rationaliser le processus d'enlèvement."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/shiprocket.rst:125
msgid ""
"Select a :guilabel:`Payment Method`. Select :guilabel:`Prepaid` to pay for "
"labels using Shiprocket account funds. Select cash on delivery "
"(:guilabel:`COD`) to ensure the receiver pays for the shipment when they "
"receive it."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/shiprocket.rst:130
msgid ""
"For **both** :guilabel:`Payment Method` selections, Shiprocket account funds "
"are deducted."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/shiprocket.rst:132
msgid ""
"If :guilabel:`COD` is selected, the payment collected upon delivery is "
"remitted according to Shiprocket's settlement cycle."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/shiprocket.rst:135
msgid ""
"In the :guilabel:`Package Type` field, select a package dimension to use for "
"shipments."
msgstr ""
"Dans le champ :guilabel:`Type de colis`, sélectionner une dimension de colis "
"à utiliser pour les expéditions."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/shiprocket.rst:137
msgid ""
"To retrieve the list of supported Shiprocket couriers, click the :icon:`fa-"
"refresh` :guilabel:`(Sync Couriers from Shiprocket)` icon next to "
"the :guilabel:`Shiprocket Couriers` field. Select the couriers to use in "
"the :guilabel:`Shiprocket Couriers` field. If this field is left blank, Odoo "
"will select the first courier based on the :ref:`courier priority <inventory/"
"shiprocket/enable-couriers>` set in the Shiprocket portal."
msgstr ""
"Pour récupérer la liste des transporteurs Shiprocket pris en charge, cliquer "
"sur l'icône :icon:`fa-refresh` :guilabel:`(Synchroniser les transporteurs "
"depuis Shiprocket)` à côté du champ :guilabel:`Transporteurs Shiprocket`. "
"Sélectionner les transporteurs à utiliser dans le champ "
":guilabel:`Transporteurs Shiprocket`. Si ce champ est laissé vide, Odoo "
"sélectionnera le premier transporteur en fonction de la :ref:`priorité du "
"transporteur <inventory/shiprocket/enable-couriers>` définie dans le portail "
"Shiprocket."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/shiprocket.rst:143
msgid ""
"To retrieve the list of Shiprocket channels, click the :icon:`fa-"
"refresh` :guilabel:`(Sync Channel from Shiprocket)` icon next to "
"the :guilabel:`Shiprocket Channel` field. In the :guilabel:`Shiprocket "
"Channel` field, select the sales channel that was created in "
"the :ref:`inventory/shiprocket/sales-channel` step."
msgstr ""
"Pour récupérer la liste des canaux Shiprocket, cliquer sur l'icône :icon:`fa-"
"refresh` :guilabel:`(Synchroniser le canal depuis Shiprocket)` à côté du "
"champ :guilabel:`Canal Shiprocket`. Dans le champ :guilabel:`Canal "
"Shiprocket`, sélectionner le canal de vente qui a été créé à l'étape "
":ref:`inventory/shiprocket/sales-channel`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/shiprocket.rst:None
msgid "Complete the fields of the form to make the shipping method available."
msgstr ""
"Remplir les champs du formulaire pour rendre la méthode d'expédition "
"disponible."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/shiprocket.rst:152
msgid "Destination Availability tab"
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/shiprocket.rst:154
msgid ""
"Use the *Destination Availability* tab to specify the :guilabel:`Countries` "
"the shipping method applies to."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/shiprocket.rst:158
msgid ""
"Shiprocket supports deliveries to over 220 countries; only those countries "
"can be selected."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/shiprocket.rst:163
msgid ""
"To use Shiprocket to generate shipping labels, the following information "
"**must** be filled out accurately and completely in Odoo:"
msgstr ""
"Pour utiliser Shiprocket afin de générer des étiquettes d'expédition, les "
"informations suivantes **doivent** être remplies de manière précise et "
"complète dans Odoo :"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/shiprocket.rst:166
msgid ""
"**Customer information**: When creating a quotation, ensure the "
"selected :guilabel:`Customer` has a valid phone number, email address, and "
"shipping address."
msgstr ""
"**Informations client** : lors de la création d'un devis, s'assurer que "
"le :guilabel:`Client` sélectionné dispose d'un numéro de téléphone, d'une "
"adresse e-mail et d'une adresse de livraison valides."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/shiprocket.rst:169
msgid ""
"To verify, select the :guilabel:`Customer` field to open their contact page. "
"Add their shipping address in the :guilabel:`Contact` field, along with "
"their :guilabel:`Mobile` number and :guilabel:`Email` address."
msgstr ""
"Pour vérifier, sélectionnez le champ :guilabel:`Client` pour ouvrir sa page "
"de contact. Ajoutez son adresse de livraison dans le champ "
":guilabel:`Contact`, ainsi que son numéro de :guilabel:`Portable` et son "
"adresse :guilabel:`E-mail`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/shiprocket.rst:172
msgid ""
"**Product weight**: Ensure all products in a delivery order have a "
"specified :guilabel:`Weight` in the *Inventory* tab of their product form. "
"Refer to the :ref:`inventory/shipping_receiving/configure-weight` "
"documentation for detailed instructions."
msgstr ""
"**Poids du produit** : assurez-vous que tous les produits d'un bon de "
"livraison ont un :guilabel:`Poids` spécifié dans l'onglet *Inventaire* de "
"leur fiche produit. Consultez la documentation :ref:`inventory/"
"shipping_receiving/configure-weight` pour des instructions détaillées."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/shiprocket.rst:175
msgid ""
"**Warehouse address**: By default all packages are sent from the specified "
"address in the warehouse. Make sure to set the :guilabel:`Address` in the "
"warehouse form with a valid phone number and email address."
msgstr ""
"**Adresse de l'entrepôt** : par défaut, tous les colis sont envoyés depuis "
"l'adresse spécifiée dans l'entrepôt. Assurez-vous de définir "
"l':guilabel:`Adresse` dans le formulaire de l'entrepôt avec un numéro de "
"téléphone et une adresse e-mail valides."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/shiprocket.rst:180
msgid "Generate a Shiprocket label"
msgstr "Générer une étiquette Shiprocket"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/shiprocket.rst:182
msgid ""
"When a quotation is created in Odoo, add the Shiprocket shipping method by "
"clicking the :guilabel:`Add shipping` button."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/shiprocket.rst:185
msgid ""
"In the *Add a shipping method* pop-up window, select :guilabel:`Shiprocket` "
"in the :guilabel:`Shipping Method` field. Calculate the shipping rate by "
"clicking :guilabel:`Get rate`. Finally, click :guilabel:`Add` to include the "
"cost of shipping to the sales order line, labeled as the *delivery product*."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/shiprocket.rst:None
msgid "Add Shiprocket shipping to a sales order."
msgstr "Ajouter l'expédition Shiprocket à une commande client."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/shiprocket.rst:194
msgid ""
"Automatically calculate shipping costs for Shiprocket in both the **Sales** "
"and **eCommerce** applications."
msgstr ""
"Calculer automatiquement les frais d'expédition pour Shiprocket dans les "
"applications **Ventes** et **eCommerce**."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/shiprocket.rst:197
#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/starshipit_shipping.rst:202
msgid ""
"Then, :guilabel:`Validate` the delivery. Shipping label documents are "
"automatically generated in the chatter, which includes the following:"
msgstr ""
"Ensuite, :guilabel:`Valider` la livraison. Les documents d'étiquettes "
"d'expédition sont automatiquement générés dans le fil de discussion, ce qui "
"inclut les éléments suivants :"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/shiprocket.rst:200
msgid "**Shipping labels**, depending on the number of packages"
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/shiprocket.rst:201
msgid "**Tracking numbers**, if the selected courier supports it"
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/shiprocket.rst:None
msgid "After the delivery is validated, a label is generated."
msgstr "Une fois la livraison validée, une étiquette est générée."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/shiprocket.rst:207
msgid ""
"If the shipment is too heavy for the Shiprocket service that is configured, "
"the weight is split to simulate multiple packages. Products must be put in "
"different packages to validate the transfer and generate labels."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/shiprocket.rst:212
#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/starshipit_shipping.rst:240
msgid "Cancellations"
msgstr "Annulations"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/shiprocket.rst:214
msgid ""
"If a delivery order is cancelled in Odoo, it is automatically archived in "
"Shiprocket. However, the cancellation will not be sent to the courier "
"itself, so make sure to log in to the courier's platform to handle the "
"cancellation manually."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/shiprocket.rst:219
msgid "Turn on Shiprocket integration"
msgstr "Activer l'intégration Shiprocket"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/shiprocket.rst:221
msgid ""
"After the Shiprocket connection is set up, use the smart buttons at the top "
"of the form to publish, turn on production mode, or activate debug logging."
msgstr ""
"Une fois la connexion Shiprocket configurée, utilisez les boutons "
"intelligents en haut du formulaire pour publier, activer le mode production "
"ou activer la journalisation de débogage."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/shiprocket.rst:224
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Unpublished/Published`: Click this smart button to make this "
"shipping method available on the **eCommerce** website."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Non publié/Publié` : cliquez sur ce bouton intelligent pour "
"rendre cette méthode d'expédition disponible sur le site Web **eCommerce**."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/shiprocket.rst:226
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Test Environment/Production Environment`: Click this smart button "
"to specify that labels are for testing only and cancelled immediately (Test) "
"or that real shipping labels can be generated and charged to the Shiprocket "
"account (Production). In the Test environment, the amount of the cancelled "
"shipment is refunded in 3 to 4 days."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/shiprocket.rst:230
msgid ""
":guilabel:`No Debug/Debug Requests`: Click this smart button to specify "
"whether API requests and responses are logged in Odoo (:doc:`turn on "
"developer mode <../../../../general/developer_mode>` and go "
"to :menuselection:`Settings app --> Technical --> Logging`)."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Aucun débogage/Déboguer les requêtes` : cliquez sur ce bouton "
"intelligent pour spécifier si les requêtes et réponses API sont enregistrées "
"dans Odoo (:doc:`activer le mode développeur <../../../../general/"
"developer_mode>` et accédez à :menuselection:`Application Paramètres --> "
"Technique --> Journalisation`)."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/starshipit_shipping.rst:3
msgid "Starshipit shipping"
msgstr "Expédition Starshipit"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/starshipit_shipping.rst:5
msgid ""
"Starshipit is a shipping service operator that facilitates the integration "
"of Australasian shipping couriers with Odoo. Once integrated, users can "
"create shipping methods that will automatically get rates from specific "
"couriers (such as Australia Post, NZ Post, DHL,...) based on predefined "
"conditions."
msgstr ""
"Starshipit est un opérateur de services d'expédition qui facilite "
"l'intégration des transporteurs australasiens avec Odoo. Une fois intégré, "
"les utilisateurs peuvent créer des modes d'expédition qui obtiendront "
"automatiquement les tarifs de transporteurs spécifiques (tels que Australia "
"Post, NZ Post, DHL, etc.) en fonction de conditions prédéfinies."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/starshipit_shipping.rst:11
msgid ":doc:`Automatically calculate shipping <../setup_configuration>`"
msgstr ""
":doc:`Calculer automatiquement les frais d'expédition <../"
"setup_configuration>`"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/starshipit_shipping.rst:12
msgid ":doc:`Integrate other third-party couriers <third_party_shipper>`"
msgstr ":doc:`Intégrer d'autres transporteurs tiers <third_party_shipper>`"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/starshipit_shipping.rst:15
msgid "Setup in Starshipit"
msgstr "Configuration dans Starshipit"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/starshipit_shipping.rst:18
msgid "Create an account and activate couriers"
msgstr "Créer un compte et activer les transporteurs"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/starshipit_shipping.rst:20
msgid ""
"To get started, go to `Starshipit's platform <https://starshipit.com/>`_ to "
"configure the account and generate the connector credentials. Log in with "
"the Starshipit account, or create a new one if needed."
msgstr ""
"Pour commencer, aller sur la `plateforme Starshipit <https://starshipit.com/"
">`_ pour configurer le compte et générer les identifiants du connecteur. Se "
"connecter avec le compte Starshipit ou en créer un nouveau si nécessaire."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/starshipit_shipping.rst:25
msgid "Pickup address configuration"
msgstr "Configuration de l'adresse d'enlèvement"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/starshipit_shipping.rst:27
msgid ""
"Once logged into the Starshipit account, navigate "
"to :menuselection:`Settings --> Pickup address`, and fill in "
"the :guilabel:`Pickup address`. Ensure this field matches the warehouse "
"address."
msgstr ""
"Une fois connecté au compte Starshipit, naviguer "
"vers :menuselection:`Settings --> Pickup address` et remplir "
"l':guilabel:`Adresse d'enlèvement`. S'assurer que ce champ correspond à "
"l'adresse de l'entrepôt."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/starshipit_shipping.rst:None
msgid "Adding addresses in the Starshipit settings."
msgstr "Ajout d'adresses dans les paramètres Starshipit."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/starshipit_shipping.rst:35
msgid "Couriers configuration"
msgstr "Configuration des transporteurs"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/starshipit_shipping.rst:37
msgid ""
"To integrate with third-party couriers, navigate to :menuselection:`Settings "
"--> Couriers`, and select :guilabel:`Couriers`."
msgstr ""
"Pour intégrer des transporteurs tiers, naviguer "
"vers :menuselection:`Settings --> Couriers` et "
"sélectionner :guilabel:`Couriers`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/starshipit_shipping.rst:45
msgid ""
"For details on integrating with different couriers, refer to `Starshipit's "
"support center <https://support.starshipit.com/hc/en-us/>`_."
msgstr ""
"Pour plus de détails sur l'intégration avec différents transporteurs, "
"consulter le `centre d'assistance Starshipit <https://support.starshipit.com/"
"hc/en-us/>`_."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/starshipit_shipping.rst:49
msgid "Checkout rates"
msgstr "Tarifs de paiement"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/starshipit_shipping.rst:51
msgid ""
"To configure shipping rate calculations, navigate "
"to :menuselection:`Settings --> Checkout rates`. The selected delivery costs "
"are automatically applied in Odoo when calculating shipping costs."
msgstr ""
"Pour configurer les calculs de tarifs d'expédition, aller "
"à :menuselection:`Paramètres --> Tarifs de paiement`. Les frais de livraison "
"sélectionnés sont automatiquement appliqués dans Odoo lors du calcul des "
"frais d'expédition."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/starshipit_shipping.rst:None
msgid "Checkout rates in the Starshipit settings."
msgstr "Tarifs de paiement dans les paramètres Starshipit."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/starshipit_shipping.rst:59
msgid "Starshipit API key"
msgstr "Clé API Starshipit"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/starshipit_shipping.rst:61
msgid ""
"Configure shipping rules to assign the correct shipping methods to orders "
"based on specific conditions."
msgstr ""
"Configurer les règles d'expédition pour attribuer les bonnes méthodes "
"d'expédition aux commandes en fonction de conditions spécifiques."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/starshipit_shipping.rst:64
msgid ""
"To create a rule, go to :menuselection:`Settings --> Rules` and "
