":guilabel:`USPS API Key`: This is the :guilabel:`Consumer Key` credential "
"for the app created in the USPS |COP| tool."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/usps.rst:99
msgid ""
":guilabel:`USPS API Secret`: This is the :guilabel:`Consumer Secret` "
"credential for the app created in the USPS |COP| tool."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/usps.rst:101
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Label Format`: Specify the file format that generated labels "
"should use."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/usps.rst:102
msgid ""
":guilabel:`USPS Package Type`: Specify or select the package type to use for "
"shipping."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/usps.rst:103
msgid ""
":guilabel:`USPS Domestic Service` or :guilabel:`USPS International Service`: "
"Specify or select the service level that should be used to generate shipping "
"labels."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/usps.rst:105
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Delivery Nature`: Specify whether the shipping method "
"is :guilabel:`Domestic` or :guilabel:`International`."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/usps.rst:107
